#ifdef FRAGMENT
#version 100

#ifdef GL_FRAGMENT_PRECISION_HIGH
    precision highp float;
#else
    precision mediump float;
#endif
precision highp int;
uniform 	float _DigiChange;
uniform 	vec4 _DigiBaseColor0;
uniform 	vec4 _DigiBaseColor1;
uniform 	vec4 _DigiST1;
uniform 	float _DigiPow;
uniform 	vec4 _MainLightPosition;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightColor;
uniform 	vec4 _Time;
uniform 	mediump vec4 unity_SpecCube0_HDR;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightShadowOffset0;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightShadowOffset1;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightShadowOffset2;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightShadowOffset3;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightShadowParams;
uniform 	mediump float _RoughNessOffset;
uniform 	mediump float _MetallicOffset;
uniform 	mediump float _NormalScale;
uniform 	mediump float _SHScale;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _SHTopColor;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _SHBotColor;
uniform 	mediump float _AOScale;
uniform 	mediump float _SHshadow;
uniform lowp sampler2D _MainTex;
uniform lowp sampler2D _MixMap;
uniform lowp sampler2D _BumpMap;
uniform highp sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
uniform lowp samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
uniform lowp sampler2D _ClothTex;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
#define SV_Target0 gl_FragData[0]
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
lowp vec3 u_xlat10_1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
lowp vec4 u_xlat10_2;
bool u_xlatb2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
float u_xlat10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
mediump float u_xlat16_20;
mediump float u_xlat16_24;
float u_xlat25;
bool u_xlatb25;
float u_xlat26;
mediump float u_xlat16_27;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat10_2.xyz = texture2D(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat10_2.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.xy = u_xlat16_0.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyw = u_xlat16_0.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyw;
    u_xlat16_24 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_24);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_24 = dot((-u_xlat1.xyz), u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_24 + u_xlat16_24;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_24)) + (-u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24 = abs(u_xlat16_24) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_24 = min(u_xlat16_24, 1.0);
    u_xlat10_1.xyz = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_27 = u_xlat10_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_27 = max(u_xlat16_27, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_27 = min(u_xlat16_27, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = (-u_xlat16_27) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_27 * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat10_2 = textureCube(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat10_2.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_3.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = log2(u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_3.x = exp2(u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_2.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat10_1.z));
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat10_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_4.x = exp2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_20 = u_xlat16_27 * u_xlat16_27;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_20 * u_xlat16_20 + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_12.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_12.x = clamp(u_xlat16_12.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_3.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_27) + u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat10_2 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat10_2.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = (-u_xlat10_2.xyz) * u_xlat16_12.xxx + u_xlat10_2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat10_2.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx + (-u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat25 = (-u_xlat16_24) + 1.0;
    u_xlat26 = log2(u_xlat16_24);
    u_xlat26 = u_xlat26 * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat26 = exp2(u_xlat26);
    u_xlat26 = (-u_xlat26) + 2.0;
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat26) * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat25 * u_xlat25;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_24 * u_xlat16_24;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat2.xyz + u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat25 = u_xlat16_0.y * u_xlat16_0.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_0.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat10 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat10 = clamp(u_xlat10, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat10) * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat25 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat25 = u_xlat25 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat5.y = u_xlat25 + 0.125;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat10 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_12.xy = max(u_xlat5.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_12.xy = u_xlat16_12.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_12.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    u_xlat25 = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat2.xy).x;
    u_xlatb25 = u_xlat25<u_xlat2.z;
    u_xlat2.x = (u_xlatb25) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat5.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    u_xlat25 = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat5.xy).x;
    u_xlatb25 = u_xlat25<u_xlat5.z;
    u_xlat2.y = (u_xlatb25) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat5.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    u_xlat25 = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat5.xy).x;
    u_xlatb25 = u_xlat25<u_xlat5.z;
    u_xlat2.z = (u_xlatb25) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat5.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    u_xlat25 = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat5.xy).x;
    u_xlatb25 = u_xlat25<u_xlat5.z;
    u_xlat2.w = (u_xlatb25) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat16_24 = dot(u_xlat2, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_24 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlatb25 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
    u_xlatb2 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
    u_xlatb25 = u_xlatb25 || u_xlatb2;
    u_xlat16_24 = (u_xlatb25) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_24;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_24 + _SHshadow;
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xxx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat2.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz / u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat1 = min(u_xlat1, vec4(100.0, 100.0, 100.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat2.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat25 = u_xlat1.w * u_xlat2.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat2.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat2.xy = u_xlat2.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat2.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat2.xy;
    u_xlat10_2.x = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat2.xy).x;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat10_2.x + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat25 = (-u_xlat25) + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat25 = clamp(u_xlat25, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat25) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_24 = (-u_xlat25) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_24) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LODFade;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightData;

UNITY_BINDING(1) uniform UnityPerMaterial {

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;

#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MatMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
uint u_xlatu0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
bool u_xlatb1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
bool u_xlatb3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
vec3 u_xlat11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
float u_xlat13;
uint u_xlatu13;
vec3 u_xlat14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
float u_xlat16;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_18;
vec3 u_xlat21;
float u_xlat26;
int u_xlati26;
bool u_xlatb26;
float u_xlat27;
mediump float u_xlat16_28;
float u_xlat34;
float u_xlat40;
mediump float u_xlat16_41;
float u_xlat42;
mediump float u_xlat16_43;
mediump float u_xlat16_45;
float u_xlat46;
float u_xlat48;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_0.w + (-_Cutoff);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb3 = !!(u_xlat16_2.x<0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb3 = u_xlat16_2.x<0.0;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb3){discard;}
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_1.z));
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = min(u_xlat16_2.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_41 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyw = u_xlat16_4.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyw;
    u_xlat16_43 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_43 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_43);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_43) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_5.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_5.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_5.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_43 = (-u_xlat16_15.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_43 = (-u_xlat16_43) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15.x = min(max(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = (-u_xlat16_0.xyz) * u_xlat16_15.xxx + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_15.x = (-u_xlat16_2.z) + u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15.x = min(max(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_43 = u_xlat16_2.z * u_xlat16_2.z;
    u_xlat42 = u_xlat16_43 * u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat14.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = abs(u_xlat16_5.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_5.x = min(u_xlat16_5.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat46 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat46 = min(max(u_xlat46, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat46 = clamp(u_xlat46, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat8.x = dot(u_xlat14.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat8.x = min(max(u_xlat8.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat8.x = clamp(u_xlat8.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat21.x = u_xlat16_4.y * u_xlat16_4.y;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat16_4.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat21.z = u_xlat21.x * 0.125 + u_xlat34;
    u_xlat21.x = u_xlat21.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat34);
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat21.zx + vec2(0.125, 0.125);
    u_xlat16_18.xy = max(u_xlat9.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_18.xy = u_xlat16_18.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_18.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat21.x = (-u_xlat16_5.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat21.x * u_xlat21.x;
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat16_45 * u_xlat16_45;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat21.xyz = (-u_xlat14.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat21.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat14.zxy) + (-u_xlat21.xyz);
    u_xlat9.x = dot(u_xlat21.xyz, u_xlat21.xyz);
    u_xlat9.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat9.x);
    u_xlat21.xyz = u_xlat21.xyz * u_xlat9.xxx;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat14.zxy) * u_xlat21.yzx;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat14.yzx) * u_xlat21.zxy + (-u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat48 = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat48 = inversesqrt(u_xlat48);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat48) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat11.x = dot(u_xlat21.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat11.y = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat11.z = dot((-u_xlat14.xyz), u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat14.x = dot(u_xlat11.xyz, u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat14.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat14.x);
    u_xlat14.xy = u_xlat14.xx * u_xlat11.xy;
    u_xlat14.xy = u_xlat14.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_10.x = (-u_xlat16_2.z) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_10.x = u_xlat16_2.z * u_xlat16_10.x;
    u_xlat16_10.x = u_xlat16_10.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = textureLod(_MatMap, u_xlat14.xy, u_xlat16_10.x).xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xyz * vec3(_MatMapMul);
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat16_43 * u_xlat16_43 + 1.0;
    u_xlat14.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat14.x;
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat14.xxx;
    u_xlat21.xyz = (-u_xlat7.xyz) + u_xlat16_15.xxx;
    u_xlat21.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_45) * u_xlat21.xyz + u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat14.xyz * u_xlat21.xyz;
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat14.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat3.x = (-u_xlat46) * u_xlat46 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16 = u_xlat16_43 * u_xlat46;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat16 * u_xlat16 + u_xlat3.x;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat16_43 / u_xlat3.x;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat3.x * u_xlat3.x;
    u_xlat16 = u_xlat16_2.z * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat3.x * u_xlat16;
    u_xlat3.x = min(u_xlat3.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = min(u_xlat16_18.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_18.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15.x = min(max(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat14.xyz * u_xlat16_15.xxx + u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_15.x);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_10.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15.x = min(max(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = max(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = min(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = (-u_xlat16_5.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat16_2.z + 1.0;
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat14.x * u_xlat14.x;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat14.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_45 = (-u_xlat14.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_45 + u_xlat27;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x / u_xlat16_45;
    u_xlat16_45 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_45 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_45);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_45) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_45 = dot(u_xlat16_10.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_45 = min(max(u_xlat16_45, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_45 = clamp(u_xlat16_45, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_45;
    u_xlat16_45 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_2.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_15.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_45;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_2.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = max(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = min(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyw = vec3(u_xlat16_41) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.x = min(_AdditionalLightsCount.x, unity_LightData.y);
    u_xlatu0 = uint(int(u_xlat16_18.x));
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat46 * u_xlat42 + (-u_xlat46);
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat13 * u_xlat46 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat13 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat13 * u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat42 / u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_28 = (-u_xlat16_2.z) * u_xlat16_2.z + 1.0;
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_28 + u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlat26 = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat16_28 + u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlat26 = u_xlat26 * u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat13 + u_xlat26;
    u_xlat16_28 = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat16_28);
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat16_28 * 0.5;
    u_xlat26 = (-u_xlat8.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat26 * u_xlat26;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat26 * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat7.y * 50.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_28 = min(max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_28 = clamp(u_xlat16_28, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_43 = (-u_xlat26) * u_xlat1.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_43);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * u_xlat14.xxx + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat13 * u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * u_xlat16_10.xyz + vec3(-6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05);
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = max(u_xlat16_18.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = min(u_xlat16_18.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * vec3(0.318309873, 0.318309873, 0.318309873) + u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyw;
    for(uint u_xlatu_loop_1 = uint(0u) ; u_xlatu_loop_1<u_xlatu0 ; u_xlatu_loop_1++)
    {
        u_xlat26 = float(int(u_xlatu_loop_1));
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb1 = !!(u_xlat26<2.0);
#else
        u_xlatb1 = u_xlat26<2.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_10.xy = (bool(u_xlatb1)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;
        u_xlat14.x = u_xlat26 + -2.0;
        u_xlat26 = (u_xlatb1) ? u_xlat26 : u_xlat14.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb26 = !!(u_xlat26<1.0);
#else
        u_xlatb26 = u_xlat26<1.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_28 = (u_xlatb26) ? u_xlat16_10.x : u_xlat16_10.y;
        u_xlati26 = int(u_xlat16_28);
        u_xlat1.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPosition[u_xlati26].xyz;
        u_xlat40 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat40 = max(u_xlat40, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat3.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat40);
        u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat3.xxx;
        u_xlat3.x = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat40);
        u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati26].x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati26].y;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat40 = min(max(u_xlat40, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat40 = clamp(u_xlat40, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * u_xlat3.x;
        u_xlat16_28 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDir[u_xlati26].xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_28 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati26].z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati26].w;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_28 = min(max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_28 = clamp(u_xlat16_28, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_28 * u_xlat16_28;
        u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * u_xlat16_28;
        u_xlat16_28 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_28 = min(max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_28 = clamp(u_xlat16_28, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * _AdditionalLightsColor[u_xlati26].xyz;
        u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat40) * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat1.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz / u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat1.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat1.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat16_1.x = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat1.xy).x;
    u_xlat14.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat27 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat27 = min(u_xlat27, 1.0);
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat14.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat27 * u_xlat14.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_1.x + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat14.x) + u_xlat1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat14.x = log2(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat14.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat14.x = exp2(u_xlat14.x);
    u_xlat14.x = (-u_xlat14.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat14.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat14.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat16_0.w;
    return;

    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;

void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat10_0.w + (-_Cutoff);
    u_xlatb3 = u_xlat16_2.x<0.0;
    if(u_xlatb3){discard;}
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(abs(u_xlat10_1.z));
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat10_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat10_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = min(u_xlat16_2.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat10_1.xyz = texture2D(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat10_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_41 * _Emissive;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _RimlightColor;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _IfDecal;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DecalRoughness;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _actorscale;

UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat5.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat2.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _MatMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
uint u_xlatu0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
bool u_xlatb1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
vec4 u_xlat6;
bool u_xlatb6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
vec3 u_xlat11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
float u_xlat14;
uint u_xlatu14;
vec3 u_xlat15;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_16;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_18;
float u_xlat19;
vec3 u_xlat21;
float u_xlat28;
int u_xlati28;
bool u_xlatb28;
float u_xlat29;
mediump float u_xlat16_30;
mediump float u_xlat16_32;
float u_xlat35;
float u_xlat43;
mediump float u_xlat16_44;
mediump float u_xlat16_45;
mediump float u_xlat16_46;
float u_xlat47;
bool u_xlatb47;
float u_xlat48;
float u_xlat51;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_1.z));
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_16.x = u_xlat16_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_30, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = min(u_xlat16_2.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_44 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_45 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_45 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_45);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_45) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat6.xy,u_xlat6.z);
    u_xlat6.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_45 = dot(u_xlat6, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_46 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat16_45 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_46;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb47 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb47 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb6 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb6 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb47 = u_xlatb47 || u_xlatb6;
    u_xlat16_45 = (u_xlatb47) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_45;
    u_xlat16_46 = (-u_xlat16_16.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_46 = (-u_xlat16_46) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_16.x = u_xlat16_16.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_16.x = min(max(u_xlat16_16.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_16.x = clamp(u_xlat16_16.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-u_xlat16_0.xyz) * u_xlat16_16.xxx + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_16.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_16.x = (-u_xlat16_2.z) + u_xlat16_46;
    u_xlat16_16.x = u_xlat16_16.x + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_16.x = min(max(u_xlat16_16.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_16.x = clamp(u_xlat16_16.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_46 = u_xlat16_2.z * u_xlat16_2.z;
    u_xlat47 = u_xlat16_46 * u_xlat16_46;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat7.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat15.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = abs(u_xlat16_4.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat48 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat48 = min(max(u_xlat48, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat48 = clamp(u_xlat48, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat7.x = dot(u_xlat15.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat7.x = min(max(u_xlat7.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat7.x = clamp(u_xlat7.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif

#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;

attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;

void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;

    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;

    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));

    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(abs(u_xlat10_1.z));
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_16.x = u_xlat10_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat10_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_30, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = min(u_xlat16_2.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat10_1.xyz = texture2D(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat10_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_44 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_45 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_45 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_45);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_45) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    u_xlat47 = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat6.xy).x;
    u_xlatb47 = u_xlat47<u_xlat6.z;
    u_xlat6.x = (u_xlatb47) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    u_xlat47 = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat7.xy).x;
    u_xlatb47 = u_xlat47<u_xlat7.z;
    u_xlat6.y = (u_xlatb47) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    u_xlat47 = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat7.xy).x;
    u_xlatb47 = u_xlat47<u_xlat7.z;
    u_xlat6.z = (u_xlatb47) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    u_xlat47 = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat7.xy).x;
    u_xlatb47 = u_xlat47<u_xlat7.z;
    u_xlat6.w = (u_xlatb47) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat16_45 = dot(u_xlat6, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_46 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat16_45 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_46;
    u_xlatb47 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
    u_xlatb6 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
    u_xlatb47 = u_xlatb47 || u_xlatb6;
    u_xlat16_45 = (u_xlatb47) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_45;
    u_xlat16_46 = (-u_xlat16_16.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_46 = (-u_xlat16_46) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_16.x = u_xlat16_16.x;
    u_xlat16_16.x = clamp(u_xlat16_16.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-u_xlat10_0.xyz) * u_xlat16_16.xxx + u_xlat10_0.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_16.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_16.x = (-u_xlat16_2.z) + u_xlat16_46;
    u_xlat16_16.x = u_xlat16_16.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_16.x = clamp(u_xlat16_16.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_46 = u_xlat16_2.z * u_xlat16_2.z;
    u_xlat47 = u_xlat16_46 * u_xlat16_46;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat7.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat15.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = abs(u_xlat16_4.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat48 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat48 = clamp(u_xlat48, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat7.x = dot(u_xlat15.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat7.x = clamp(u_xlat7.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat21.x = u_xlat16_3.y * u_xlat16_3.y;
    u_xlat35 = u_xlat16_3.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat21.z = u_xlat21.x * 0.125 + u_xlat35;
    u_xlat21.x = u_xlat21.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat35);
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat21.zx + vec2(0.125, 0.125);
    u_xlat16_18.xy = max(u_xlat9.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_18.xy = u_xlat16_18.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_18.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat21.x = (-u_xlat16_4.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat21.x * u_xlat21.x;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_18.x * u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat21.xyz = (-u_xlat15.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat21.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat15.zxy) + (-u_xlat21.xyz);
    u_xlat9.x = dot(u_xlat21.xyz, u_xlat21.xyz);
    u_xlat9.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat9.x);
    u_xlat21.xyz = u_xlat21.xyz * u_xlat9.xxx;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat15.zxy) * u_xlat21.yzx;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat15.yzx) * u_xlat21.zxy + (-u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat51 = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat51 = inversesqrt(u_xlat51);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat51) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat11.x = dot(u_xlat21.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat11.y = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat11.z = dot((-u_xlat15.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat15.x = dot(u_xlat11.xyz, u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat15.x);
    u_xlat15.xy = u_xlat15.xx * u_xlat11.xy;
    u_xlat15.xy = u_xlat15.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_32 = (-u_xlat16_2.z) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_32 = u_xlat16_2.z * u_xlat16_32;
    u_xlat16_32 = u_xlat16_32 * 6.0;
    u_xlat10_15.xyz = texture2D(_MatMap, u_xlat15.xy, u_xlat16_32).xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat10_15.xyz * vec3(_MatMapMul);
    u_xlat15.x = u_xlat16_46 * u_xlat16_46 + 1.0;
    u_xlat15.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat15.x;
    u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat15.xxx;
    u_xlat21.xyz = (-u_xlat6.xyz) + u_xlat16_16.xxx;
    u_xlat21.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xxx * u_xlat21.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat15.xyz * u_xlat21.xyz;
    u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_45) * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat5.x = (-u_xlat48) * u_xlat48 + 1.0;
    u_xlat19 = u_xlat16_46 * u_xlat48;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat19 * u_xlat19 + u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat16_46 / u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat19 = u_xlat16_2.z * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat19;
    u_xlat5.x = min(u_xlat5.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = min(u_xlat16_10.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_16.x = u_xlat16_45 + _SHshadow;
    u_xlat16_16.x = clamp(u_xlat16_16.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat15.xyz * u_xlat16_16.xxx + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_16.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_16.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_16.x);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_16.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_16.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_12.xyz);
    u_xlat16_16.x = clamp(u_xlat16_16.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_16.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = max(u_xlat16_12.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = min(u_xlat16_12.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_16.x = (-u_xlat16_4.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat15.x = u_xlat16_2.z + 1.0;
    u_xlat15.x = u_xlat15.x * u_xlat15.x;
    u_xlat29 = u_xlat15.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_18.x = (-u_xlat15.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_16.x * u_xlat16_18.x + u_xlat29;
    u_xlat16_16.x = u_xlat16_16.x / u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_18.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_18.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_18.x);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.x = dot(u_xlat16_12.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_18.x = clamp(u_xlat16_18.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_18.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_16.x * u_xlat16_2.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_16.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_16.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_16.x = u_xlat16_2.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_16.x;
    u_xlat16_16.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_16.x = u_xlat16_45 * u_xlat16_16.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_16.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat10_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_13.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;

    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat14 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat14 * u_xlat16_45;

    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat14 * u_xlat16_45;

    u_xlat16_18.xyz = min(u_xlat16_18.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));

    for(int u_xlati_loop_1 = 0 ; u_xlati_loop_1<u_xlati0 ; u_xlati_loop_1++)

        u_xlat28 = float(u_xlati_loop_1);

        u_xlat43 = u_xlat43 * u_xlat16_30;
        u_xlat16_30 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat16_30 = clamp(u_xlat16_30, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_30) * _AdditionalLightsColorDynamicIndex(u_xlati28).xyz;
        u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat43) * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
        u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);

    u_xlat15.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;

    u_xlat29 = min(u_xlat29, 1.0);

    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat15.x) + u_xlat1.x;

    u_xlat15.x = log2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat15.x = u_xlat15.x * _DigiPow;

    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat15.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx + u_xlat16_16.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat10_0.w;
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat5.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat2.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);

    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;

    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
uint u_xlatu0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
bool u_xlatb1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
vec4 u_xlat6;
bool u_xlatb6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
vec3 u_xlat11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
float u_xlat13;
uint u_xlatu13;
vec3 u_xlat14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_17;
float u_xlat26;
int u_xlati26;
bool u_xlatb26;
float u_xlat27;
mediump float u_xlat16_28;
float u_xlat40;
mediump float u_xlat16_41;
mediump float u_xlat16_42;
mediump float u_xlat16_43;
float u_xlat44;
bool u_xlatb44;
float u_xlat45;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_1.z));
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = min(u_xlat16_2.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_41 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_42 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_42 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat6.xy,u_xlat6.z);
    u_xlat6.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_42 = dot(u_xlat6, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_43 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_42 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_43;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb44 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb44 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb6 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb6 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb44 = u_xlatb44 || u_xlatb6;
    u_xlat16_42 = (u_xlatb44) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_43 = (-u_xlat16_15.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_43 = (-u_xlat16_43) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15.x = min(max(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-u_xlat16_0.xyz) * u_xlat16_15.xxx + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_15.x = (-u_xlat16_2.z) + u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15.x = min(max(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_43 = u_xlat16_2.z * u_xlat16_2.z;
    u_xlat44 = u_xlat16_43 * u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat7.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat14.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = abs(u_xlat16_4.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat45 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat45 = min(max(u_xlat45, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat45 = clamp(u_xlat45, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat14.x = dot(u_xlat14.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat14.x = min(max(u_xlat14.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat14.x = clamp(u_xlat14.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat16_3.y * u_xlat16_3.y;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat16_3.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat7.x = u_xlat27 * 0.125 + u_xlat40;
    u_xlat7.x = u_xlat7.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat27 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat40);
    u_xlat7.y = u_xlat27 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_17.xy = max(u_xlat7.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_17.xy = u_xlat16_17.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_17.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat27 = (-u_xlat16_4.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat27 * u_xlat27;
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_17.x * u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _GlossyEnvironmentColor.xyz;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat16_43 * u_xlat16_43 + 1.0;
    u_xlat27 = float(1.0) / u_xlat27;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * vec3(u_xlat27);
    u_xlat11.xyz = (-u_xlat6.xyz) + u_xlat16_15.xxx;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xxx * u_xlat11.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz * u_xlat11.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat27 = (-u_xlat45) * u_xlat45 + 1.0;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat16_43 * u_xlat45;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat40 * u_xlat40 + u_xlat27;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat16_43 / u_xlat27;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat27 * u_xlat27;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat16_2.z * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat27 * u_xlat40;
    u_xlat27 = min(u_xlat27, 100.0);
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat27) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = min(u_xlat16_9.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_42 + _SHshadow;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15.x = min(max(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz * u_xlat16_15.xxx + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_15.x);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_10.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15.x = min(max(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = max(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = min(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = (-u_xlat16_4.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat16_2.z + 1.0;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat27 * u_xlat27;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat27 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-u_xlat27) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_17.x + u_xlat40;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x / u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_17.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_17.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_17.x);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.x = dot(u_xlat16_10.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_17.x = min(max(u_xlat16_17.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_17.x = clamp(u_xlat16_17.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_2.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_15.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_2.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_15.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_42 * u_xlat16_15.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = max(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = min(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyw = vec3(u_xlat16_41) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_42 = min(_AdditionalLightsCount.x, unity_LightData.y);
    u_xlatu0 = uint(int(u_xlat16_42));
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat45 * u_xlat44 + (-u_xlat45);
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat13 * u_xlat45 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat13 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat13 * u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat44 / u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_28 = (-u_xlat16_2.z) * u_xlat16_2.z + 1.0;
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_28 + u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlat26 = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat16_28 + u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlat26 = u_xlat26 * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat13 + u_xlat26;
    u_xlat16_28 = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat16_28);
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat16_28 * 0.5;
    u_xlat26 = (-u_xlat14.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat26 * u_xlat26;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat26 * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat6.y * 50.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_28 = min(max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_28 = clamp(u_xlat16_28, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-u_xlat26) * u_xlat1.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * u_xlat16_17.xxx;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * u_xlat14.xxx + u_xlat16_17.xyz;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat13 * u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * u_xlat16_17.xyz + vec3(-6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05);
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = max(u_xlat16_17.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = min(u_xlat16_17.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * vec3(0.318309873, 0.318309873, 0.318309873) + u_xlat16_17.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyw;
    for(uint u_xlatu_loop_1 = uint(0u) ; u_xlatu_loop_1<u_xlatu0 ; u_xlatu_loop_1++)
    {
        u_xlat26 = float(int(u_xlatu_loop_1));
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb1 = !!(u_xlat26<2.0);
#else
        u_xlatb1 = u_xlat26<2.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_9.xy = (bool(u_xlatb1)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;
        u_xlat14.x = u_xlat26 + -2.0;
        u_xlat26 = (u_xlatb1) ? u_xlat26 : u_xlat14.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb26 = !!(u_xlat26<1.0);
#else
        u_xlatb26 = u_xlat26<1.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_28 = (u_xlatb26) ? u_xlat16_9.x : u_xlat16_9.y;
        u_xlati26 = int(u_xlat16_28);
        u_xlat1.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPosition[u_xlati26].xyz;
        u_xlat40 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat40 = max(u_xlat40, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat5.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat40);
        u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat5.xxx;
        u_xlat5.x = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat40);
        u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati26].x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati26].y;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat40 = min(max(u_xlat40, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat40 = clamp(u_xlat40, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * u_xlat5.x;
        u_xlat16_28 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDir[u_xlati26].xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_28 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati26].z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati26].w;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_28 = min(max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_28 = clamp(u_xlat16_28, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_28 * u_xlat16_28;
        u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * u_xlat16_28;
        u_xlat16_28 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_28 = min(max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_28 = clamp(u_xlat16_28, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * _AdditionalLightsColor[u_xlati26].xyz;
        u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat40) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
        u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat1.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz / u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat1.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat1.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat16_1.x = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat1.xy).x;
    u_xlat14.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat27 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat27 = min(u_xlat27, 1.0);
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat14.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat27 * u_xlat14.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_1.x + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat14.x) + u_xlat1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat14.x = log2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat14.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat14.x = exp2(u_xlat14.x);
    u_xlat14.x = (-u_xlat14.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat14.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat14.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat16_0.w;
    return;
}

void main()

UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat5.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat2.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}
