    u_xlat0.x = (-u_xlat0.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat12 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_24.x = (-u_xlat12) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_24.x = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_24.x + u_xlat33;
    u_xlat16_24.x = u_xlat16_35 / u_xlat16_24.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_24.x * u_xlat16_13.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_24.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_24.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_24.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_24.x * u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = clamp(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_24.x = u_xlat16_13.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_24.x;
    u_xlat16_24.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_24.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat10_5.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat10_5.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;

    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = max(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = min(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_41) * u_xlat10_5.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat10_5.w;
    u_xlat33 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat33 = min(u_xlat33, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat1.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat1.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat1.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat1.xy).x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat10_1 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat33 = (-u_xlat33) + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat33 = clamp(u_xlat33, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35 = (-u_xlat33) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_35) + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat5.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat2.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

#endif

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec4 u_xlat0;
bool u_xlatb0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump float u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
vec3 u_xlat12;
bool u_xlatb12;
float u_xlat13;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_22;
float u_xlat24;
float u_xlat25;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_26;
mediump float u_xlat16_38;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
mediump float u_xlat16_40;
mediump float u_xlat16_44;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat0.xy,u_xlat0.z);
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat1.xy,u_xlat1.z);
    u_xlat0.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat1.xy,u_xlat1.z);
    u_xlat0.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat1.xy,u_xlat1.z);
    u_xlat0.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat0, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_14.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_14.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb12 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb12 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlatb12 || u_xlatb0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_2.x + _SHshadow;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_14.x = min(max(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_14.x = clamp(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat0.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = min(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat12.xyz, u_xlat12.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_26.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_4.xyw = u_xlat16_26.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyw = u_xlat16_26.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyw;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyw;
    u_xlat16_26.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_26.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_26.x);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_26.xxx * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat0.x = min(max(u_xlat0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat12.x = (-u_xlat0.x) * u_xlat0.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_26.x = u_xlat16_5.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_26.x = max(u_xlat16_26.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_26.x = min(u_xlat16_26.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_26.x * u_xlat16_26.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat16_38;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x + u_xlat12.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_38 / u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat12.x = u_xlat16_38 * u_xlat16_38 + 1.0;
    u_xlat12.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat12.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat24 = u_xlat16_26.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat24;
    u_xlat0.x = min(u_xlat0.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_5.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_38;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_39 = min(max(u_xlat16_39, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_39 = clamp(u_xlat16_39, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_38 = (-u_xlat16_38) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_38 = (-u_xlat16_38) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_38 = (-u_xlat16_26.x) + u_xlat16_38;
    u_xlat24 = u_xlat16_26.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat24 = u_xlat24 * u_xlat24;
    u_xlat16_26.x = u_xlat16_38 + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_26.x = min(max(u_xlat16_26.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_26.x = clamp(u_xlat16_26.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_6 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat7.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-u_xlat16_6.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_39) + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat0.x = min(max(u_xlat0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat9.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat9.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_38 = log2(abs(u_xlat16_5.z));
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_5.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_38 * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_38 = exp2(u_xlat16_38);
    u_xlat16_38 = min(u_xlat16_38, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_38) * _GlossyEnvironmentColor.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = u_xlat12.xxx * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_40 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_40 = abs(u_xlat16_40) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_40 = min(u_xlat16_40, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat16_40) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_44 * u_xlat16_44;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_26.xxx + (-u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_44) * u_xlat1.xyz + u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = u_xlat0.xyw * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_4.y * u_xlat16_4.y;
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat16_4.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat25 = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + u_xlat13;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat13);
    u_xlat1.y = u_xlat1.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat25 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_10.xy = max(u_xlat1.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xy = u_xlat16_10.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_10.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_22.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_38) * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat0.xyw * u_xlat16_14.xxx + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_14.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_14.x);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_8.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_14.x = min(max(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_14.x = clamp(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = max(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = min(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_14.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_14.x);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.x = dot(u_xlat16_8.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_14.x = min(max(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_14.x = clamp(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_38 * u_xlat16_14.x;
    u_xlat16_26.x = (-u_xlat16_40) + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.x = log2(u_xlat16_40);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat0.x = exp2(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.x = (-u_xlat0.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat0.xyw = u_xlat0.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat24 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_38 = (-u_xlat24) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_26.x * u_xlat16_38 + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_26.x = u_xlat16_26.x / u_xlat16_38;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_26.x * u_xlat16_14.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_26.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_26.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_26.x;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_26.x * u_xlat16_14.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_14.x = min(max(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_14.x = clamp(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_26.x = u_xlat16_14.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_14.x * u_xlat16_14.x;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_14.x * u_xlat16_26.x;
    u_xlat16_26.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_26.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_14.x;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_6.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_14.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = max(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = min(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat16_6.w;
    u_xlat24 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat24 = min(u_xlat24, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat24 = u_xlat24 * u_xlat1.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat1.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat1.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat1.xy).x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_1 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat24 = (-u_xlat24) + u_xlat1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat24 = min(max(u_xlat24, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat24 = clamp(u_xlat24, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat24) * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_38 = (-u_xlat24) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyw * vec3(u_xlat16_38) + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    return;
}

    u_xlat16_26.x = u_xlat16_14.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_14.x * u_xlat16_14.x;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_14.x * u_xlat16_26.x;
    u_xlat16_26.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_26.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_14.x;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat10_6.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat10_6.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_14.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = max(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = min(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat10_6.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat10_6.w;
    u_xlat24 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat24 = min(u_xlat24, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat24 = u_xlat24 * u_xlat1.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat1.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat1.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat1.xy).x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat10_1 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat24 = (-u_xlat24) + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat24 = clamp(u_xlat24, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat24) * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_38 = (-u_xlat24) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyw * vec3(u_xlat16_38) + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}

UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat5.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat2.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(7) uniform mediump sampler2D _RampTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec4 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
vec3 u_xlat10;
mediump float u_xlat16_10;
bool u_xlatb10;
float u_xlat11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
mediump float u_xlat16_15;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_16;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_22;
mediump float u_xlat16_25;
float u_xlat31;
mediump float u_xlat16_32;
mediump float u_xlat16_33;
float u_xlat34;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
float u_xlat37;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat0.xy,u_xlat0.z);
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat1.xy,u_xlat1.z);
    u_xlat0.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat1.xy,u_xlat1.z);
    u_xlat0.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat1.xy,u_xlat1.z);
    u_xlat0.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat0, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_12.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_12.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb10 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb10 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlatb10 || u_xlatb0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_2.x + _SHshadow;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_12.x = min(max(u_xlat16_12.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_12.x = clamp(u_xlat16_12.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_3.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_3.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_3.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_22.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_22.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_22.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_22.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_22.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_22.x);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_22.x = dot((-u_xlat10.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_22.x = u_xlat16_22.x + u_xlat16_22.x;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * (-u_xlat16_22.xxx) + (-u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat16_22.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat16_22.x = abs(u_xlat16_22.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_32 = u_xlat16_0.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_22.y = max(u_xlat16_32, 0.0399999991);

    u_xlat16_33 = (-u_xlat16_22.y) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_22.y * u_xlat16_33;
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_33 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_4 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_33);

    u_xlat16_33 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_33 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_33 = max(u_xlat16_33, 0.0);

    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_33 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;

    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_33 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;

    u_xlat16_33 = log2(abs(u_xlat16_0.z));
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_33 * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_33 = exp2(u_xlat16_33);
    u_xlat16_33 = min(u_xlat16_33, 1.0);

    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_22.y * u_xlat16_22.y;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_35 + 1.0;
    u_xlat10.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat10.x;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat10.xxx;
    u_xlat10.x = (-u_xlat16_22.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat10.x * u_xlat10.x;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_15 = u_xlat16_0.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_25 = u_xlat16_0.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_25 = u_xlat16_25 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-u_xlat16_15) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_15 = u_xlat16_15;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15 = min(max(u_xlat16_15, 0.0), 1.0);
#else

    u_xlat16_6.x = (-u_xlat16_6.x) + 1.0;

    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x + 1.0;

    u_xlat16_6.x = min(max(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_6.x = clamp(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_15) * u_xlat7.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);

    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * u_xlat8.xyz + u_xlat7.xyz;

    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat37 + 0.125;

    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_16.xyz + u_xlat4.xyz;

    u_xlat31 = inversesqrt(u_xlat31);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat31) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else

#endif
    u_xlat11 = (-u_xlat1.x) * u_xlat1.x + 1.0;

    u_xlat16_5.xyw = min(u_xlat16_5.xyw, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat1.xyw * u_xlat16_5.xyw;

    u_xlat16_1.xyw = texture(_RampTex, u_xlat8.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyw * u_xlat16_16.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyw = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyw + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyw = u_xlat4.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xxx + u_xlat16_5.xyw;
    u_xlat16_12.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_12.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_12.x);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_12.x = min(max(u_xlat16_12.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_12.x = clamp(u_xlat16_12.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyw * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = max(u_xlat16_6.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = min(u_xlat16_6.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_5.xyw = u_xlat16_5.xyw + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_12.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_12.x);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;

    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_33 * u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_32 = (-u_xlat16_22.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = log2(u_xlat16_22.x);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat1.x = exp2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + 2.0;

    u_xlat16_22.x = (-u_xlat1.z) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_22.x = u_xlat16_32 * u_xlat16_22.x + u_xlat4.x;
    u_xlat16_22.x = u_xlat16_32 / u_xlat16_22.x;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_22.x * u_xlat16_12.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_22.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_22.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_22.x;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_22.x * u_xlat16_12.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_12.x = min(max(u_xlat16_12.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_12.x = clamp(u_xlat16_12.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_22.x = u_xlat16_12.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_22.x;
    u_xlat16_22.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_22.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_12.x;

    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;

    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyw;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_25) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat16_0.w;
    u_xlat0.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat0.x = min(u_xlat0.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat10.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat10.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat10.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat10.x = fract(_Time.x);

    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyw * vec3(u_xlat16_32) + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    return;

#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];

attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;

varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;

vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

uniform highp sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
uniform lowp samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;

varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
#define SV_Target0 gl_FragData[0]
vec4 u_xlat0;
lowp vec4 u_xlat10_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
lowp vec4 u_xlat10_1;
bool u_xlatb1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
lowp vec4 u_xlat10_4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
vec3 u_xlat7;

mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;

lowp float u_xlat10_10;
bool u_xlatb10;
float u_xlat11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
mediump float u_xlat16_15;

float u_xlat31;

mediump float u_xlat16_33;
float u_xlat34;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
float u_xlat37;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat0.xy).x;
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat0.x<u_xlat0.z;
    u_xlat0.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat1.xy).x;
    u_xlatb1 = u_xlat1.x<u_xlat1.z;
    u_xlat0.y = (u_xlatb1) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat1.xy).x;
    u_xlatb1 = u_xlat1.x<u_xlat1.z;
    u_xlat0.z = (u_xlatb1) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat1.xy).x;
    u_xlatb1 = u_xlat1.x<u_xlat1.z;
    u_xlat0.w = (u_xlatb1) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat0, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_12.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlatb0 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
    u_xlatb10 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlatb10 || u_xlatb0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_2.x + _SHshadow;
    u_xlat16_12.x = clamp(u_xlat16_12.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_3.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_3.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat10_4.xyz = texture2D(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_4.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_22.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_22.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_22.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_22.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_22.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_22.x);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_22.x = dot((-u_xlat10.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_22.x = u_xlat16_22.x + u_xlat16_22.x;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * (-u_xlat16_22.xxx) + (-u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat16_22.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat16_22.x = abs(u_xlat16_22.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_32 = u_xlat10_0.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_22.y = max(u_xlat16_32, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_22.xy = min(u_xlat16_22.xy, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_33 = (-u_xlat16_22.y) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_22.y * u_xlat16_33;
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_33 * 6.0;
    u_xlat10_4 = textureCube(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_33);
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat10_4.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_33 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_33 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_33 = max(u_xlat16_33, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_33 = log2(u_xlat16_33);
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_33 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_33 = exp2(u_xlat16_33);
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_33 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat10_4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_33);
    u_xlat16_33 = log2(abs(u_xlat10_0.z));
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_33 * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_33 = exp2(u_xlat16_33);
    u_xlat16_33 = min(u_xlat16_33, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_33) * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_22.y * u_xlat16_22.y;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_35 + 1.0;
    u_xlat10.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat10.x;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat10.xxx;
    u_xlat10.x = (-u_xlat16_22.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat10.x * u_xlat10.x;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_15 = u_xlat10_0.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_25 = u_xlat10_0.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_25 = u_xlat16_25 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-u_xlat16_15) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_15 = u_xlat16_15;
    u_xlat16_15 = clamp(u_xlat16_15, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-u_xlat16_6.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-u_xlat16_22.y) + u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_6.x = clamp(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_15) * u_xlat7.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_16.xyz = (-u_xlat10_0.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_15) + u_xlat10_0.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xxx + (-u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * u_xlat8.xyz + u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat31 = u_xlat16_3.y * u_xlat16_3.y;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat16_3.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat37 = u_xlat31 * 0.125 + u_xlat34;
    u_xlat31 = u_xlat31 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat34);
    u_xlat8.y = u_xlat31 + 0.125;
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat37 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_5.xy = max(u_xlat8.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_5.xy = u_xlat16_5.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_5.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_33) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_16.xyz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat31 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat31 = inversesqrt(u_xlat31);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat31) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat11 = (-u_xlat1.x) * u_xlat1.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x + u_xlat11;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_35 / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat16_22.y * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat1.z = u_xlat16_22.y + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.xz = u_xlat1.xz * u_xlat1.xz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat11;
    u_xlat1.x = min(u_xlat1.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat1.xyw = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat34 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat7.x = u_xlat34;
    u_xlat7.x = clamp(u_xlat7.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat34 * 0.5 + 0.5;
    u_xlat1.xyw = u_xlat1.xyw * u_xlat7.xxx;
    u_xlat1.xyw = u_xlat1.xyw * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = u_xlat1.xyw * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat7.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyw = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyw = u_xlat16_5.xyw * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_5.xyw = min(u_xlat16_5.xyw, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat1.xyw * u_xlat16_5.xyw;
    u_xlat8.y = 0.5;
    u_xlat10_1.xyw = texture2D(_RampTex, u_xlat8.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyw * u_xlat16_16.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyw = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyw + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyw = u_xlat4.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xxx + u_xlat16_5.xyw;
    u_xlat16_12.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_12.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_12.x);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_12.x = clamp(u_xlat16_12.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyw * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = max(u_xlat16_6.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = min(u_xlat16_6.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_5.xyw = u_xlat16_5.xyw + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_12.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_12.x);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.x = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_12.x = clamp(u_xlat16_12.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_33 * u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_32 = (-u_xlat16_22.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = log2(u_xlat16_22.x);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat1.x = exp2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat1.xyw = u_xlat1.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat4.x = u_xlat1.z * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_22.x = (-u_xlat1.z) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_22.x = u_xlat16_32 * u_xlat16_22.x + u_xlat4.x;
    u_xlat16_22.x = u_xlat16_32 / u_xlat16_22.x;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_22.x * u_xlat16_12.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_22.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_22.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_22.x;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_22.x * u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_12.x = clamp(u_xlat16_12.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_22.x = u_xlat16_12.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_22.x;
    u_xlat16_22.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_22.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat10_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = max(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = min(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyw;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_25) * u_xlat10_0.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat10_0.w;
    u_xlat0.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat0.x = min(u_xlat0.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat10.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat10.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat10.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat10.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat10.xy = u_xlat10.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat10.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat10.xy;
    u_xlat10_10 = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat10.xy).x;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat10_10 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat0.x = (-u_xlat0.x) + u_xlat10.x;
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_32 = (-u_xlat0.x) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyw * vec3(u_xlat16_32) + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    return;
}

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Smoothness;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cutoff;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _BumpScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _EmissionColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SketchHalftoneMin;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SketchHalftoneMax;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SketchColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RampThreshold;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RampSmooth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AOScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ActorScaleAttribute;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FurShape;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Rimlightoffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _viweoffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHshadow;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _RimLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MatMapMul;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

#endif

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
float u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
vec3 u_xlat11;
mediump float u_xlat16_11;
float u_xlat12;
mediump float u_xlat16_14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
mediump float u_xlat16_20;
mediump float u_xlat16_24;
mediump float u_xlat16_25;
mediump float u_xlat16_30;
float u_xlat32;
float u_xlat33;
mediump float u_xlat16_34;
float u_xlat36;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1 = max(u_xlat1, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1 = inversesqrt(u_xlat1);
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(u_xlat1) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.xy = u_xlat16_0.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyw = u_xlat16_0.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyw;
    u_xlat16_30 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_30 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_30);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_30) * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_30 = dot((-u_xlat11.xyz), u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_30 + u_xlat16_30;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_30)) + (-u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_30 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_30 = abs(u_xlat16_30) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_30 = min(u_xlat16_30, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_34 = max(u_xlat16_34, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_34 = min(u_xlat16_34, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-u_xlat16_34) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_3 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_3.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = exp2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_5.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_1.z));
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_5.x = exp2(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_5.x = min(u_xlat16_5.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xxx;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_34;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_15.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat11.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat11.x;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat11.xxx;
    u_xlat11.x = (-u_xlat16_30) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat11.x * u_xlat11.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_24 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_25 = (-u_xlat16_14) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_14;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_14 = min(max(u_xlat16_14, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_14 = clamp(u_xlat16_14, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_25 = (-u_xlat16_25) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_25 = (-u_xlat16_34) + u_xlat16_25;
    u_xlat16_25 = u_xlat16_25 + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_25 = min(max(u_xlat16_25, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_25 = clamp(u_xlat16_25, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_14) * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-u_xlat16_1.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_14) + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_25) + (-u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat8.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat16_0.y * u_xlat16_0.y;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat16_0.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat32 * 0.125 + u_xlat33;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat32 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat33);
    u_xlat8.y = u_xlat32 + 0.125;
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat36 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat8.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat32 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat32 = inversesqrt(u_xlat32);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat32) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat2.x = min(max(u_xlat2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat2.x = clamp(u_xlat2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat12 = (-u_xlat2.x) * u_xlat2.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * u_xlat2.x + u_xlat12;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_15.x / u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat16_34 * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat2.z = u_xlat16_34 + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.xz = u_xlat2.xz * u_xlat2.xz;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * u_xlat12;
    u_xlat2.x = min(u_xlat2.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat33 = min(max(u_xlat33, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat33 = clamp(u_xlat33, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xyw * vec3(u_xlat33);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xyw * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xyw * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat6.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = min(u_xlat16_7.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat2.xyw * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyw = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_15.x);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_15.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15.x = min(max(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyw * u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = max(u_xlat16_15.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = min(u_xlat16_15.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyw = u_xlat16_4.xyw + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_15.x);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.x = dot(u_xlat16_15.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_0.x = min(max(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_10.x = (-u_xlat16_30) + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = log2(u_xlat16_30);
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat2.x = exp2(u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat2.x = (-u_xlat2.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat2.z * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_20 = (-u_xlat2.z) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_20 = u_xlat16_10.x * u_xlat16_20 + u_xlat3.x;
    u_xlat16_10.x = u_xlat16_10.x / u_xlat16_20;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_10.x * u_xlat16_0.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_10.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_10.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_10.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_10.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_0.x = min(max(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_10.x = u_xlat16_0.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_10.x;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_0.xxx;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = max(u_xlat16_0.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = min(u_xlat16_0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyw;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat16_1.w;
    u_xlat1 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat1 = min(u_xlat1, 1.0);
    u_xlat11.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat11.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 * u_xlat11.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat11.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat11.xy = u_xlat11.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat11.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat11.xy;
    u_xlat16_11 = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat11.xy).x;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat16_11 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat1 = (-u_xlat1) + u_xlat11.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1 = min(max(u_xlat1, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1 = clamp(u_xlat1, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(u_xlat1);
    u_xlat16_30 = (-u_xlat1) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat2.xyw * vec3(u_xlat16_30) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    return;
}

#endif
"

void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;

    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];

    gl_Position = u_xlat1;

    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);

    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;

    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;

    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;

    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyw * u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = max(u_xlat16_15.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = min(u_xlat16_15.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyw = u_xlat16_4.xyw + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_15.x);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.x = dot(u_xlat16_15.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_10.x = (-u_xlat16_30) + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = log2(u_xlat16_30);
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat2.x = exp2(u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat2.x = (-u_xlat2.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat2.z * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_20 = (-u_xlat2.z) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_20 = u_xlat16_10.x * u_xlat16_20 + u_xlat3.x;
    u_xlat16_10.x = u_xlat16_10.x / u_xlat16_20;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_10.x * u_xlat16_0.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_10.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_10.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_10.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_10.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_10.x = u_xlat16_0.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_10.x;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat10_1.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_0.xxx;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = max(u_xlat16_0.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = min(u_xlat16_0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyw;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat10_1.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat10_1.w;
    u_xlat1 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat1 = min(u_xlat1, 1.0);
    u_xlat11.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat11.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 * u_xlat11.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat11.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat11.xy = u_xlat11.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat11.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat11.xy;
    u_xlat10_11 = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat11.xy).x;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat10_11 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat1 = (-u_xlat1) + u_xlat11.x;
    u_xlat1 = clamp(u_xlat1, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(u_xlat1);
    u_xlat16_30 = (-u_xlat1) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat2.xyw * vec3(u_xlat16_30) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}

UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat5.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat2.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;

in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec4 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
vec3 u_xlat10;
mediump float u_xlat16_10;
bool u_xlatb10;
float u_xlat11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
mediump float u_xlat16_15;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_16;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_22;
mediump float u_xlat16_25;
float u_xlat31;
mediump float u_xlat16_32;
mediump float u_xlat16_33;
float u_xlat34;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
float u_xlat37;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat0.xy,u_xlat0.z);
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat1.xy,u_xlat1.z);
    u_xlat0.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);

    u_xlat16_5.xyw = u_xlat4.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xxx + u_xlat16_5.xyw;

    u_xlat16_12.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_12.x = min(max(u_xlat16_12.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else

#endif
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyw * u_xlat16_6.xyz;

    u_xlat16_22.x = u_xlat16_32 / u_xlat16_22.x;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_22.x * u_xlat16_12.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_22.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_22.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_22.x;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_22.x * u_xlat16_12.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_12.x = min(max(u_xlat16_12.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_12.x = clamp(u_xlat16_12.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_22.x = u_xlat16_12.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_22.x;
    u_xlat16_22.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_22.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = max(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = min(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyw;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_25) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat16_0.w;
    u_xlat0.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat0.x = min(u_xlat0.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat10.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat10.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat10.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat10.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat10.xy = u_xlat10.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat10.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat10.xy;
    u_xlat16_10 = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat10.xy).x;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat16_10 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat0.x = (-u_xlat0.x) + u_xlat10.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat0.x = min(max(u_xlat0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_32 = (-u_xlat0.x) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyw * vec3(u_xlat16_32) + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    return;
}

SubProgram "gles " {
Keywords { "ENABLE_POST_TONE" "_DEBUG_OFF" "_IFFUR_OFF" "_IFRAMP_OFF" "_MAIN_LIGHT_SHADOWS" "_SHADOWS_SOFT" "_SHTYPE_LERP" }
"// hash: c82441c31adcda64
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];

uniform 	mediump float _FurTilling;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;

vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT

#ifdef GL_FRAGMENT_PRECISION_HIGH
    precision highp float;
#else
    precision mediump float;

precision highp int;
uniform 	float _DigiChange;

varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;

varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
#define SV_Target0 gl_FragData[0]
vec4 u_xlat0;
lowp vec4 u_xlat10_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
vec4 u_xlat1;

mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
