uniform lowp sampler2D _MainTex;
uniform lowp sampler2D _MixMap;
uniform lowp sampler2D _BumpMap;
uniform lowp sampler2D _MatMap;
uniform lowp sampler2D _ClothTex;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
#define SV_Target0 gl_FragData[0]
vec3 u_xlat0;
lowp vec4 u_xlat10_0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
lowp vec3 u_xlat10_2;
bool u_xlatb2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
lowp vec3 u_xlat10_3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
lowp vec3 u_xlat10_5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
vec2 u_xlat9;
lowp float u_xlat10_9;
float u_xlat11;
float u_xlat12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
mediump float u_xlat16_24;
float u_xlat27;
mediump float u_xlat16_28;
float u_xlat29;
mediump float u_xlat16_33;
void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat10_0.w + (-_Cutoff);
    u_xlatb2 = u_xlat16_1.x<0.0;
    if(u_xlatb2){discard;}
    u_xlat16_1.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_1.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_1.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat2.x = max(u_xlat2.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * u_xlat2.xxx;
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-u_xlat2.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat2.zxy) + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat29 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat29 = inversesqrt(u_xlat29);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat29) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = (-u_xlat2.zxy) * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat4.xyz = (-u_xlat2.yzx) * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat29 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat29 = inversesqrt(u_xlat29);
    u_xlat4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat29) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat10_5.xyz = texture2D(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat10_5.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.xy = u_xlat16_1.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_1.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyw = u_xlat16_1.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyw;
    u_xlat16_28 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_28 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_28);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat4.y = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat4.x = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat4.z = dot((-u_xlat2.xyz), u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_28 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_28 = abs(u_xlat16_28) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_28 = min(u_xlat16_28, 1.0);
    u_xlat2.x = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat2.xy = u_xlat2.xx * u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat2.xy = u_xlat2.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10_3.xyz = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat10_3.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_6.x = max(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_6.x = min(u_xlat16_6.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_15.x = (-u_xlat16_6.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat10_2.xyz = texture2D(_MatMap, u_xlat2.xy, u_xlat16_15.x).xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat10_2.xyz * vec3(_MatMapMul);
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_6.x * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_7.x * u_xlat16_7.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * u_xlat2.xxx;
    u_xlat29 = (-u_xlat16_28) + 1.0;
    u_xlat12 = log2(u_xlat16_28);
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat12 * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat12 = exp2(u_xlat12);
    u_xlat12 = (-u_xlat12) + 2.0;
    u_xlat4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat12) * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat29 * u_xlat29;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_28 * u_xlat16_28;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat10_3.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_24 = log2(abs(u_xlat10_3.z));
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_24 * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_24 = exp2(u_xlat16_24);
    u_xlat16_24 = min(u_xlat16_24, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_33 = (-u_xlat16_15.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_33 = (-u_xlat16_33) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-u_xlat16_6.x) + u_xlat16_33;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_6.x = clamp(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * u_xlat3.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-u_xlat10_0.xyz) * u_xlat16_15.xxx + u_xlat10_0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat10_0.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = (-u_xlat3.xyz) + u_xlat16_6.xxx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat16_1.y * u_xlat16_1.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat11 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat11 = clamp(u_xlat11, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat11) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat27 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat27 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat3.y = u_xlat27 + 0.125;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat11 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_6.xy = max(u_xlat3.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_6.xy = u_xlat16_6.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_6.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyw = u_xlat16_6.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat16_6.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_28 = _SHshadow + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_28 = clamp(u_xlat16_28, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_28);
    u_xlat0.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = min(u_xlat16_7.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat0.x = min(u_xlat0.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat9.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat9.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat9.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat9.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat9.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat10_9 = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat9.xy).x;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat10_9 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat0.x = (-u_xlat0.x) + u_xlat9.x;
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_28 = (-u_xlat0.x) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_28) + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

#endif

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MatMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec2 u_xlat9;
mediump float u_xlat16_9;
float u_xlat10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
mediump float u_xlat16_21;
mediump float u_xlat16_24;
float u_xlat25;
mediump float u_xlat16_29;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = (-u_xlat1.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat2.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat1.zxy) + (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat25 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat25 = inversesqrt(u_xlat25);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat25) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-u_xlat1.zxy) * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-u_xlat1.yzx) * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat25 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat25 = inversesqrt(u_xlat25);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat25) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.xy = u_xlat16_0.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyw = u_xlat16_0.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyw;
    u_xlat16_24 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_24);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat3.y = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat3.x = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot((-u_xlat1.xyz), u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24 = abs(u_xlat16_24) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_24 = min(u_xlat16_24, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xx * u_xlat3.xy;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_2.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_5.x = max(u_xlat16_5.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_5.x = min(u_xlat16_5.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_13.x = (-u_xlat16_5.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = textureLod(_MatMap, u_xlat1.xy, u_xlat16_13.x).xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(_MatMapMul);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_6.x * u_xlat16_6.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat25 = (-u_xlat16_24) + 1.0;
    u_xlat10 = log2(u_xlat16_24);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat10 = exp2(u_xlat10);
    u_xlat10 = (-u_xlat10) + 2.0;
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat10) * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat25 * u_xlat25;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_24 * u_xlat16_24;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_2.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_21 = log2(abs(u_xlat16_2.z));
    u_xlat16_21 = u_xlat16_21 * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_21 = exp2(u_xlat16_21);
    u_xlat16_21 = min(u_xlat16_21, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_29 = (-u_xlat16_13.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_13.x = min(max(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_13.x = clamp(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_29 = (-u_xlat16_29) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-u_xlat16_5.x) + u_xlat16_29;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_5.x = min(max(u_xlat16_5.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_5.x = clamp(u_xlat16_5.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = (-u_xlat16_2.xyz) * u_xlat16_13.xxx + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat16_2.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = (-u_xlat4.xyz) + u_xlat16_5.xxx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat2.xyz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat25 = u_xlat16_0.y * u_xlat16_0.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_0.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat10 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat10 = min(max(u_xlat10, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat10 = clamp(u_xlat10, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat10) * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat25 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat25 = u_xlat25 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat4.y = u_xlat25 + 0.125;
    u_xlat4.x = u_xlat10 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_5.xy = max(u_xlat4.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_5.xy = u_xlat16_5.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_5.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyw = u_xlat16_5.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_21) * u_xlat16_5.xyw;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_24 = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_24 = min(max(u_xlat16_24, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_24 = clamp(u_xlat16_24, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = min(u_xlat16_6.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = min(u_xlat1.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat9.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat9.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat9.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat9.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat9.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat16_9 = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat9.xy).x;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat16_9 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + u_xlat9.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_24 = (-u_xlat1.x) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_24) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    return;
}

#endif
"

SubProgram "gles " {
Keywords { "ENABLE_POST_TONE" "PGAME_SHADER_LEVEL_LOWEST" "_DEBUG_OFF" "_IFFUR_OFF" "_IFRAMP_OFF" "_SHTYPE_LERP" }

"// hash: 6348cd0366abc72f
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
uniform 	mediump float _FurTilling;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT
#version 100

#ifdef GL_FRAGMENT_PRECISION_HIGH
    precision highp float;
#else
    precision mediump float;
#endif
precision highp int;
uniform 	float _DigiChange;
uniform 	vec4 _DigiBaseColor0;
uniform 	vec4 _DigiBaseColor1;
uniform 	vec4 _DigiST1;
uniform 	float _DigiPow;
uniform 	vec4 _MainLightPosition;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightColor;
uniform 	vec4 _Time;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[4];
uniform 	mediump float _RoughNessOffset;
uniform 	mediump float _MetallicOffset;
uniform 	mediump float _NormalScale;
uniform 	mediump float _SHScale;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _SHTopColor;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _SHBotColor;
uniform 	mediump float _AOScale;
uniform 	mediump float _SHshadow;
uniform 	mediump float _MatMapMul;
uniform lowp sampler2D _MainTex;
uniform lowp sampler2D _MixMap;
uniform lowp sampler2D _BumpMap;
uniform lowp sampler2D _MatMap;
uniform lowp sampler2D _ClothTex;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
#define SV_Target0 gl_FragData[0]
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
lowp vec3 u_xlat10_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
lowp vec4 u_xlat10_2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
lowp vec3 u_xlat10_4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec2 u_xlat9;
lowp float u_xlat10_9;
float u_xlat10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
mediump float u_xlat16_21;
mediump float u_xlat16_24;
float u_xlat25;
mediump float u_xlat16_29;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = (-u_xlat1.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat2.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat1.zxy) + (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat25 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat25 = inversesqrt(u_xlat25);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat25) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-u_xlat1.zxy) * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-u_xlat1.yzx) * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat25 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat25 = inversesqrt(u_xlat25);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat25) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat10_4.xyz = texture2D(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat10_4.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.xy = u_xlat16_0.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyw = u_xlat16_0.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyw;
    u_xlat16_24 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_24);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat3.y = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat3.x = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot((-u_xlat1.xyz), u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24 = abs(u_xlat16_24) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_24 = min(u_xlat16_24, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xx * u_xlat3.xy;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10_2.xyz = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat10_2.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_5.x = max(u_xlat16_5.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_5.x = min(u_xlat16_5.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_13.x = (-u_xlat16_5.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat10_1.xyz = texture2D(_MatMap, u_xlat1.xy, u_xlat16_13.x).xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz * vec3(_MatMapMul);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_6.x * u_xlat16_6.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat25 = (-u_xlat16_24) + 1.0;
    u_xlat10 = log2(u_xlat16_24);
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat10 * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat10 = exp2(u_xlat10);
    u_xlat10 = (-u_xlat10) + 2.0;
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat10) * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat25 * u_xlat25;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_24 * u_xlat16_24;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat10_2.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_21 = log2(abs(u_xlat10_2.z));
    u_xlat16_21 = u_xlat16_21 * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_21 = exp2(u_xlat16_21);
    u_xlat16_21 = min(u_xlat16_21, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_29 = (-u_xlat16_13.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = clamp(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_29 = (-u_xlat16_29) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-u_xlat16_5.x) + u_xlat16_29;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = clamp(u_xlat16_5.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat10_2 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat10_2.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = (-u_xlat10_2.xyz) * u_xlat16_13.xxx + u_xlat10_2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat10_2.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = (-u_xlat4.xyz) + u_xlat16_5.xxx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat2.xyz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat25 = u_xlat16_0.y * u_xlat16_0.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_0.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat10 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat10 = clamp(u_xlat10, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat10) * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat25 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat25 = u_xlat25 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat4.y = u_xlat25 + 0.125;
    u_xlat4.x = u_xlat10 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_5.xy = max(u_xlat4.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_5.xy = u_xlat16_5.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_5.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyw = u_xlat16_5.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_21) * u_xlat16_5.xyw;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_24 = _SHshadow + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_24 = clamp(u_xlat16_24, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = min(u_xlat16_6.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = min(u_xlat1.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat9.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat9.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat9.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat9.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat9.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat10_9 = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat9.xy).x;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat10_9 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + u_xlat9.x;
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_24 = (-u_xlat1.x) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_24) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(std140)
#endif

#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTexMouth_ST;

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
vec2 u_xlat6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat9;
mediump float u_xlat16_11;
mediump float u_xlat16_19;
mediump float u_xlat16_24;
float u_xlat26;
mediump float u_xlat16_27;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.xy = u_xlat16_0.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyw = u_xlat16_0.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyw;
    u_xlat16_24 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_24);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_24 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24 = abs(u_xlat16_24) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_24 = min(u_xlat16_24, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat16_24) + 1.0;
    u_xlat9.x = log2(u_xlat16_24);
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat9.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat9.x = exp2(u_xlat9.x);
    u_xlat9.x = (-u_xlat9.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat9.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_24 * u_xlat16_24;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_2.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_3.x = max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_11 = u_xlat16_2.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_19 = log2(abs(u_xlat16_2.z));
    u_xlat16_19 = u_xlat16_19 * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_3.z = exp2(u_xlat16_19);
    u_xlat16_3.xz = min(u_xlat16_3.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_27 = (-u_xlat16_11) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_11 = u_xlat16_11;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_11 = min(max(u_xlat16_11, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_11 = clamp(u_xlat16_11, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_27 = (-u_xlat16_27) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_27 = (-u_xlat16_3.x) + u_xlat16_27;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_3.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_27 + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_11) * u_xlat4.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = (-u_xlat16_2.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_11) + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat16_2.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat2.xyz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.zzz * _GlossyEnvironmentColor.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_0.y * u_xlat16_0.y;
    u_xlat26 = u_xlat16_0.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat4.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat4.x = min(max(u_xlat4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat4.x = clamp(u_xlat4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat4.xxx * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat4.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + u_xlat26;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat26);
    u_xlat6.y = u_xlat1.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat4.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_3.xy = max(u_xlat6.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_24 = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_24 = min(max(u_xlat16_24, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_24 = clamp(u_xlat16_24, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = min(u_xlat16_5.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = min(u_xlat1.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat2.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat2.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat2.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat2.xy = u_xlat2.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat2.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat2.xy;
    u_xlat16_2.x = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat2.xy).x;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_2.x + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + u_xlat2.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_24 = (-u_xlat1.x) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat9.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_24) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    return;
}

#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
uniform 	mediump float _FurTilling;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

    u_xlat16_27 = (-u_xlat16_27) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_27 = (-u_xlat16_3.x) + u_xlat16_27;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_3.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_27 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat10_2 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat10_2.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_11) * u_xlat4.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = (-u_xlat10_2.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_11) + u_xlat10_2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat10_2.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat2.xyz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.zzz * _GlossyEnvironmentColor.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_0.y * u_xlat16_0.y;
    u_xlat26 = u_xlat16_0.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat4.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat4.x = clamp(u_xlat4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat4.xxx * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat4.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + u_xlat26;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat26);
    u_xlat6.y = u_xlat1.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat4.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_3.xy = max(u_xlat6.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_24 = _SHshadow + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_24 = clamp(u_xlat16_24, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = min(u_xlat16_5.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = min(u_xlat1.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat2.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat2.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat2.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat2.xy = u_xlat2.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat2.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat2.xy;
    u_xlat10_2.x = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat2.xy).x;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat10_2.x + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_24 = (-u_xlat1.x) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat9.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_24) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    return;
}

#endif
"

UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _RampTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
vec2 u_xlat7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
vec2 u_xlat9;
mediump float u_xlat16_9;
float u_xlat10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
mediump float u_xlat16_12;
mediump float u_xlat16_20;
mediump float u_xlat16_24;
float u_xlat25;
float u_xlat26;
mediump float u_xlat16_27;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.xy = u_xlat16_0.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyw = u_xlat16_0.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyw;
    u_xlat16_24 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_24);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_24 = dot((-u_xlat1.xyz), u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_24 + u_xlat16_24;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_24)) + (-u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24 = abs(u_xlat16_24) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_24 = min(u_xlat16_24, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_27 = u_xlat16_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_27 = max(u_xlat16_27, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_27 = min(u_xlat16_27, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = (-u_xlat16_27) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_27 * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_2 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_2.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_3.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = log2(u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_3.x = exp2(u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_1.z));
    u_xlat16_12 = u_xlat16_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_4.x = exp2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_20 = u_xlat16_27 * u_xlat16_27;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_20 * u_xlat16_20 + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_12) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_12 = u_xlat16_12;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_12 = min(max(u_xlat16_12, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_12 = clamp(u_xlat16_12, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_3.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_27) + u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_12) * u_xlat5.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = (-u_xlat16_2.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_12) + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat16_2.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx + (-u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat25 = (-u_xlat16_24) + 1.0;
    u_xlat26 = log2(u_xlat16_24);
    u_xlat26 = u_xlat26 * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat26 = exp2(u_xlat26);
    u_xlat26 = (-u_xlat26) + 2.0;
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat26) * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat25 * u_xlat25;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_24 * u_xlat16_24;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat2.xyz + u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat25 = u_xlat16_0.y * u_xlat16_0.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_0.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat10 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat10 * 0.5 + 0.5;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat25 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat25 = u_xlat25 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat7.y = u_xlat25 + 0.125;
    u_xlat7.x = u_xlat10 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_0.xy = max(u_xlat7.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_0.xy = u_xlat16_0.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.x = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_0.x = min(max(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xxx * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat5.y = 0.5;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = texture(_RampTex, u_xlat5.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = min(u_xlat1.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat9.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat9.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat9.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat9.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat9.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat16_9 = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat9.xy).x;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat16_9 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + u_xlat9.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_24 = (-u_xlat1.x) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_24) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    return;
}

{

    u_xlat1.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat5.y = 0.5;
    u_xlat10_1.xyz = texture2D(_RampTex, u_xlat5.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = min(u_xlat1.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat9.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat9.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat9.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat9.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat9.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat10_9 = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat9.xy).x;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat10_9 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + u_xlat9.x;
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_24 = (-u_xlat1.x) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_24) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}

UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec2 u_xlat9;
mediump float u_xlat16_9;
float u_xlat10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
mediump float u_xlat16_20;
mediump float u_xlat16_24;
float u_xlat25;
float u_xlat26;
mediump float u_xlat16_27;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.xy = u_xlat16_0.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyw = u_xlat16_0.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyw;
    u_xlat16_24 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_24);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_24 = dot((-u_xlat1.xyz), u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_24 + u_xlat16_24;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_24)) + (-u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24 = abs(u_xlat16_24) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_24 = min(u_xlat16_24, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_27 = u_xlat16_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_27 = max(u_xlat16_27, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_27 = min(u_xlat16_27, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = (-u_xlat16_27) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_27 * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_2 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_2.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_3.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = log2(u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_3.x = exp2(u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_1.z));
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_4.x = exp2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_20 = u_xlat16_27 * u_xlat16_27;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_20 * u_xlat16_20 + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_12.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_12.x = min(max(u_xlat16_12.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_12.x = clamp(u_xlat16_12.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_3.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_27) + u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x + 1.0;

    u_xlat16_3.x = min(max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif

    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = (-u_xlat16_2.xyz) * u_xlat16_12.xxx + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat16_2.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx + (-u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat25 = (-u_xlat16_24) + 1.0;
    u_xlat26 = log2(u_xlat16_24);
    u_xlat26 = u_xlat26 * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat26 = exp2(u_xlat26);
    u_xlat26 = (-u_xlat26) + 2.0;

    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat25 * u_xlat25;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_24 * u_xlat16_24;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat2.xyz + u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat25 = u_xlat16_0.y * u_xlat16_0.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_0.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat10 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat10 = min(max(u_xlat10, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat10 = clamp(u_xlat10, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif

    u_xlat25 = u_xlat25 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat5.y = u_xlat25 + 0.125;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat10 + 0.125;

    u_xlat16_24 = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_24 = min(max(u_xlat16_24, 0.0), 1.0);
#else

    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = min(u_xlat1.x, 1.0);

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightIndices[2];

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SpecCube0_HDR;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_DynamicLightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAg;

#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};

UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec2 u_xlat9;
mediump float u_xlat16_9;
float u_xlat10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
mediump float u_xlat16_20;
mediump float u_xlat16_24;
float u_xlat25;
float u_xlat26;
mediump float u_xlat16_27;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.xy = u_xlat16_0.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyw = u_xlat16_0.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyw;
    u_xlat16_24 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_24);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_24 = dot((-u_xlat1.xyz), u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_24 + u_xlat16_24;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_24)) + (-u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24 = abs(u_xlat16_24) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_24 = min(u_xlat16_24, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_27 = u_xlat16_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_27 = max(u_xlat16_27, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_27 = min(u_xlat16_27, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = (-u_xlat16_27) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_27 * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_2 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_2.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_3.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = log2(u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_3.x = exp2(u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_1.z));
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_4.x = exp2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_20 = u_xlat16_27 * u_xlat16_27;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_20 * u_xlat16_20 + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_12.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_12.x = min(max(u_xlat16_12.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_12.x = clamp(u_xlat16_12.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_3.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_27) + u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = (-u_xlat16_2.xyz) * u_xlat16_12.xxx + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat16_2.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx + (-u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat25 = (-u_xlat16_24) + 1.0;
    u_xlat26 = log2(u_xlat16_24);
    u_xlat26 = u_xlat26 * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat26 = exp2(u_xlat26);
    u_xlat26 = (-u_xlat26) + 2.0;
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat26) * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat25 * u_xlat25;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_24 * u_xlat16_24;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat2.xyz + u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat25 = u_xlat16_0.y * u_xlat16_0.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_0.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat10 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat10 = min(max(u_xlat10, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat10 = clamp(u_xlat10, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat10) * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat10 = u_xlat25 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat25 = u_xlat25 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat5.y = u_xlat25 + 0.125;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat10 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_12.xy = max(u_xlat5.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_12.xy = u_xlat16_12.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_12.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_24 = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_24 = min(max(u_xlat16_24, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_24 = clamp(u_xlat16_24, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = min(u_xlat1.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat9.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat9.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat9.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat9.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat9.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat9.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat9.xy;
    u_xlat16_9 = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat9.xy).x;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat16_9 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + u_xlat9.x;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AOScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ActorScaleAttribute;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FurShape;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Rimlightoffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _viweoffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHshadow;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _RimLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MatMapMul;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

#endif

precision highp float;

#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
