UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MatMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
float u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
bool u_xlatb2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
vec2 u_xlat11;
mediump float u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
vec3 u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_18;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_19;
mediump float u_xlat16_20;
mediump float u_xlat16_23;
mediump float u_xlat16_29;
mediump float u_xlat16_34;
float u_xlat35;
float u_xlat36;
mediump float u_xlat16_40;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_0.w + (-_Cutoff);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb2 = !!(u_xlat16_1.x<0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb2 = u_xlat16_1.x<0.0;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb2){discard;}
    u_xlat16_1.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_1.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_1.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat2.x = max(u_xlat2.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat13.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * u_xlat2.xxx;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * u_xlat2.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = (-u_xlat13.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat13.zxy) + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat2.x = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat2.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = (-u_xlat13.zxy) * u_xlat4.yzx;
    u_xlat5.xyz = (-u_xlat13.yzx) * u_xlat4.zxy + (-u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat2.x = dot(u_xlat5.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat2.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.xy = u_xlat16_1.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_1.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyw = u_xlat16_1.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyw;
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat5.y = dot(u_xlat5.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat5.x = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat5.z = dot((-u_xlat13.xyz), u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat13.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = abs(u_xlat16_34) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_34 = min(u_xlat16_34, 1.0);
    u_xlat2.x = dot(u_xlat5.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat2.xy = u_xlat2.xx * u_xlat5.xy;
    u_xlat2.xy = u_xlat2.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_4 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_4.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_7.x = max(u_xlat16_7.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_7.x = min(u_xlat16_7.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_18.x = (-u_xlat16_7.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_18.x * u_xlat16_7.x;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_18.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = textureLod(_MatMap, u_xlat2.xy, u_xlat16_18.x).xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(_MatMapMul);
    u_xlat16_8.x = u_xlat16_7.x * u_xlat16_7.x;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_8.x * u_xlat16_8.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz * u_xlat2.xxx;
    u_xlat35 = (-u_xlat16_34) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat35 * u_xlat35;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_18.x * u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_29 = u_xlat16_4.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_40 = (-u_xlat16_29) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_29 = u_xlat16_29;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_29 = min(max(u_xlat16_29, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_29 = clamp(u_xlat16_29, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_40 = (-u_xlat16_40) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_40 = (-u_xlat16_7.x) + u_xlat16_40;
    u_xlat16_40 = u_xlat16_40 + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_40 = min(max(u_xlat16_40, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_40 = clamp(u_xlat16_40, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_29) * u_xlat5.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_19.xyz = (-u_xlat16_0.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_29) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = (-u_xlat5.xyz) + vec3(u_xlat16_40);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz + u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat35 = u_xlat16_1.y * u_xlat16_1.y;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat16_1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat4.x = u_xlat35 * 0.125 + u_xlat36;
    u_xlat35 = u_xlat35 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat36);
    u_xlat6.y = u_xlat35 + 0.125;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat4.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_18.xy = max(u_xlat6.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_18.xy = u_xlat16_18.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_18.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_4.z));
    u_xlat16_20 = u_xlat16_4.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_20 = u_xlat16_20 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_9.x = u_xlat16_9.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_9.x = exp2(u_xlat16_9.x);
    u_xlat16_9.x = min(u_xlat16_9.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xxx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz * u_xlat16_19.xyz + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.x = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_18.x = min(max(u_xlat16_18.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_18.x = clamp(u_xlat16_18.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat35 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat35 = inversesqrt(u_xlat35);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat35) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat35 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat35 = min(max(u_xlat35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat35 = clamp(u_xlat35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat3.x = (-u_xlat35) * u_xlat35 + 1.0;
    u_xlat35 = u_xlat16_8.x * u_xlat35;
    u_xlat35 = u_xlat35 * u_xlat35 + u_xlat3.x;
    u_xlat35 = u_xlat16_8.x / u_xlat35;
    u_xlat35 = u_xlat35 * u_xlat35;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat16_7.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat14 = u_xlat16_7.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat14 = u_xlat14 * u_xlat14;
    u_xlat35 = u_xlat35 * u_xlat3.x;
    u_xlat35 = min(u_xlat35, 100.0);
    u_xlat3.xzw = vec3(u_xlat35) * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat35 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat35 = min(max(u_xlat35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat35 = clamp(u_xlat35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat3.xzw = vec3(u_xlat35) * u_xlat3.xzw;
    u_xlat16_7.xzw = vec3(u_xlat35) * u_xlat16_19.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xzw = u_xlat3.xzw * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xzw = u_xlat3.xzw * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat4.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = min(u_xlat16_8.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat3.xzw * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xzw = u_xlat16_7.xzw * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * u_xlat16_18.xxx + u_xlat16_7.xzw;
    u_xlat16_40 = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_40 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_40);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_40) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_40 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_8.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_40 = min(max(u_xlat16_40, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_40 = clamp(u_xlat16_40, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_40) * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = max(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = min(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_40 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_40 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_40);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_40) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = dot(u_xlat16_8.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_9.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_12.x = (-u_xlat16_34) + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = log2(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat2.x = exp2(u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat2.x = (-u_xlat2.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat35 = u_xlat14 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_23 = (-u_xlat14) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_23 = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_23 + u_xlat35;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x / u_xlat16_23;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_1.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_12.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_12.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_1.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = min(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_20) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat16_0.w;
    u_xlat0 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat0 = min(u_xlat0, 1.0);
    u_xlat11.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat11.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 * u_xlat11.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat11.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat11.xy = u_xlat11.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat11.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat11.xy;
    u_xlat16_11 = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat11.xy).x;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat16_11 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat0 = (-u_xlat0) + u_xlat11.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat0 = min(max(u_xlat0, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat0 = clamp(u_xlat0, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat0) * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = (-u_xlat0) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_34) + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    return;
}

#endif
"

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;

vec4 u_xlat0;

float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;

    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;

    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;

    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat3.xzw * u_xlat16_8.xyz;

    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * u_xlat16_18.xxx + u_xlat16_7.xzw;

    u_xlat16_40 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_40);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_40) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_40 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_8.xyz);
    u_xlat16_40 = clamp(u_xlat16_40, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_40) * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = max(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = min(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_40 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_40 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_40);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_40) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = dot(u_xlat16_8.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_9.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_12.x = (-u_xlat16_34) + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = log2(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat2.x = exp2(u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat2.x = (-u_xlat2.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat35 = u_xlat14 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_23 = (-u_xlat14) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_23 = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_23 + u_xlat35;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x / u_xlat16_23;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_1.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_12.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_12.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_1.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat10_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = min(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_20) * u_xlat10_0.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat10_0.w;
    u_xlat0 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat0 = min(u_xlat0, 1.0);
    u_xlat11.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat11.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 * u_xlat11.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat11.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat11.xy = u_xlat11.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat11.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat11.xy;
    u_xlat10_11 = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat11.xy).x;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat10_11 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat0 = (-u_xlat0) + u_xlat11.x;
    u_xlat0 = clamp(u_xlat0, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat0) * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = (-u_xlat0) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_34) + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}

UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MatMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump float u_xlat16_2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
vec3 u_xlat12;
float u_xlat13;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_17;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_18;
mediump float u_xlat16_20;
mediump float u_xlat16_22;
mediump float u_xlat16_28;
mediump float u_xlat16_33;
float u_xlat34;
float u_xlat35;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-u_xlat12.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat12.zxy) + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = (-u_xlat12.zxy) * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat4.xyz = (-u_xlat12.yzx) * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.xy = u_xlat16_0.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyw = u_xlat16_0.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyw;
    u_xlat16_33 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_33 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_33);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_33) * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat4.y = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat4.x = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat4.z = dot((-u_xlat12.xyz), u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_33 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat12.xyz);
    u_xlat16_33 = abs(u_xlat16_33) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_33 = min(u_xlat16_33, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xx * u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_3 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_3.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_6.x = max(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_6.x = min(u_xlat16_6.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-u_xlat16_6.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_17.x * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_17.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = textureLod(_MatMap, u_xlat1.xy, u_xlat16_17.x).xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(_MatMapMul);
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_6.x * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_7.x * u_xlat16_7.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat34 = (-u_xlat16_33) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat34 * u_xlat34;
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_17.x * u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_3.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_39 = (-u_xlat16_28) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_28;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_28 = min(max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_28 = clamp(u_xlat16_28, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_39 = (-u_xlat16_39) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_39 = (-u_xlat16_6.x) + u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_39 = min(max(u_xlat16_39, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_39 = clamp(u_xlat16_39, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * u_xlat5.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = (-u_xlat16_4.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_28) + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = (-u_xlat5.xyz) + vec3(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xxx * u_xlat8.xyz + u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat16_0.y * u_xlat16_0.y;
    u_xlat35 = u_xlat16_0.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat34 * 0.125 + u_xlat35;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat34 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat35);
    u_xlat8.y = u_xlat34 + 0.125;
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat3.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_17.xy = max(u_xlat8.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_17.xy = u_xlat16_17.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_17.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_3.z));
    u_xlat16_20 = u_xlat16_3.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_20 = u_xlat16_20 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_9.x = u_xlat16_9.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_9.x = exp2(u_xlat16_9.x);
    u_xlat16_9.x = min(u_xlat16_9.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xxx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xyz * u_xlat16_18.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.x = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_17.x = min(max(u_xlat16_17.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_17.x = clamp(u_xlat16_17.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat34 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat34 = inversesqrt(u_xlat34);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat34 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat34 = min(max(u_xlat34, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat34 = clamp(u_xlat34, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat2.x = (-u_xlat34) * u_xlat34 + 1.0;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat16_7.x * u_xlat34;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat34 * u_xlat34 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat16_7.x / u_xlat34;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat34 * u_xlat34;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_6.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat16_6.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat13 * u_xlat13;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat34 * u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat34 = min(u_xlat34, 100.0);
    u_xlat2.xzw = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat34 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat34 = min(max(u_xlat34, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat34 = clamp(u_xlat34, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat2.xzw = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat2.xzw;
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xzw = u_xlat2.xzw * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xzw = u_xlat2.xzw * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat3.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = min(u_xlat16_7.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat2.xzw * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = u_xlat16_6.xzw * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat16_17.xxx + u_xlat16_6.xzw;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_7.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_39 = min(max(u_xlat16_39, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_39 = clamp(u_xlat16_39, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = max(u_xlat16_7.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = min(u_xlat16_7.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.x = dot(u_xlat16_7.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_0.x = min(max(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_9.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_11.x = (-u_xlat16_33) + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = log2(u_xlat16_33);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat1.x = exp2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat13 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_22 = (-u_xlat13) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_22 = u_xlat16_11.x * u_xlat16_22 + u_xlat34;
    u_xlat16_11.x = u_xlat16_11.x / u_xlat16_22;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_11.x * u_xlat16_0.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_11.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_11.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_11.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_11.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_0.x = min(max(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_11.x = u_xlat16_0.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_11.x;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_4.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat16_0.xxx;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = max(u_xlat16_0.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = min(u_xlat16_0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_20) * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat16_4.w;
    u_xlat34 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat34 = min(u_xlat34, 1.0);
    u_xlat2.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat34 * u_xlat2.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat2.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat2.xy = u_xlat2.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat2.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat2.xy;
    u_xlat16_2 = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat2.xy).x;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_2 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat34 = (-u_xlat34) + u_xlat2.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat34 = min(max(u_xlat34, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat34 = clamp(u_xlat34, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(u_xlat34);
    u_xlat16_33 = (-u_xlat34) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_33) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    return;
}

#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;

varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;

vec4 u_xlat0;

float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-u_xlat12.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat12.zxy) + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = (-u_xlat12.zxy) * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat4.xyz = (-u_xlat12.yzx) * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat10_5.xyz = texture2D(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat10_5.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.xy = u_xlat16_0.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyw = u_xlat16_0.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyw;
    u_xlat16_33 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_33 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_33);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_33) * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat4.y = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat4.x = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat4.z = dot((-u_xlat12.xyz), u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_33 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat12.xyz);
    u_xlat16_33 = abs(u_xlat16_33) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_33 = min(u_xlat16_33, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xx * u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10_3 = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat10_3.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_6.x = max(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_6.x = min(u_xlat16_6.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-u_xlat16_6.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_17.x * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_17.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat10_1.xyz = texture2D(_MatMap, u_xlat1.xy, u_xlat16_17.x).xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz * vec3(_MatMapMul);
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_6.x * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_7.x * u_xlat16_7.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat34 = (-u_xlat16_33) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat34 * u_xlat34;
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_17.x * u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat10_3.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_39 = (-u_xlat16_28) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_28;
    u_xlat16_28 = clamp(u_xlat16_28, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_39 = (-u_xlat16_39) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_39 = (-u_xlat16_6.x) + u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_39 = clamp(u_xlat16_39, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat10_4 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat10_4.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * u_xlat5.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = (-u_xlat10_4.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_28) + u_xlat10_4.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = (-u_xlat5.xyz) + vec3(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xxx * u_xlat8.xyz + u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat16_0.y * u_xlat16_0.y;
    u_xlat35 = u_xlat16_0.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat34 * 0.125 + u_xlat35;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat34 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat35);
    u_xlat8.y = u_xlat34 + 0.125;
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat3.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_17.xy = max(u_xlat8.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_17.xy = u_xlat16_17.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_17.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.x = log2(abs(u_xlat10_3.z));
    u_xlat16_20 = u_xlat10_3.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_20 = u_xlat16_20 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_9.x = u_xlat16_9.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_9.x = exp2(u_xlat16_9.x);
    u_xlat16_9.x = min(u_xlat16_9.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xxx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xyz * u_xlat16_18.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.x = _SHshadow + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17.x = clamp(u_xlat16_17.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat34 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat34 = inversesqrt(u_xlat34);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat34 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat34 = clamp(u_xlat34, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat2.x = (-u_xlat34) * u_xlat34 + 1.0;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat16_7.x * u_xlat34;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat34 * u_xlat34 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat16_7.x / u_xlat34;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat34 * u_xlat34;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_6.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat16_6.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat13 * u_xlat13;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat34 * u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat34 = min(u_xlat34, 100.0);
    u_xlat2.xzw = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat34 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat34 = clamp(u_xlat34, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat2.xzw = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat2.xzw;
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xzw = u_xlat2.xzw * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xzw = u_xlat2.xzw * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat3.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = min(u_xlat16_7.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat2.xzw * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xzw = u_xlat16_6.xzw * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat16_17.xxx + u_xlat16_6.xzw;

    u_xlat16_39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_7.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = clamp(u_xlat16_39, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = max(u_xlat16_7.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = min(u_xlat16_7.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.x = dot(u_xlat16_7.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_9.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_11.x = (-u_xlat16_33) + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = log2(u_xlat16_33);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat1.x = exp2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat13 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_22 = (-u_xlat13) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_22 = u_xlat16_11.x * u_xlat16_22 + u_xlat34;
    u_xlat16_11.x = u_xlat16_11.x / u_xlat16_22;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_11.x * u_xlat16_0.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_11.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_11.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_11.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_11.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_11.x = u_xlat16_0.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_11.x;

    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat16_0.xxx;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = max(u_xlat16_0.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = min(u_xlat16_0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_20) * u_xlat10_4.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat10_4.w;
    u_xlat34 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat34 = min(u_xlat34, 1.0);
    u_xlat2.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat34 * u_xlat2.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat2.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat2.xy = u_xlat2.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat2.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat2.xy;
    u_xlat10_2 = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat2.xy).x;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat10_2 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat34 = (-u_xlat34) + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat34 = clamp(u_xlat34, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(u_xlat34);
    u_xlat16_33 = (-u_xlat34) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_33) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;

void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;

    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;

    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;

    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);

    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;

    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT

precision highp float;

uniform 	float _DigiChange;

#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS

#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec2 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
mediump float u_xlat16_7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
vec2 u_xlat10;
mediump float u_xlat16_10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
vec3 u_xlat16;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_17;
float u_xlat20;
mediump float u_xlat16_21;
mediump float u_xlat16_23;
mediump float u_xlat16_31;
mediump float u_xlat16_32;
mediump float u_xlat16_33;
float u_xlat34;
float u_xlat35;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.xy = u_xlat16_1.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyw = u_xlat16_1.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyw;
    u_xlat16_31 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_31 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_31);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_31) * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_1.y * u_xlat16_1.y;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat16_1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat20 = u_xlat0.x * 0.125 + u_xlat10.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat10.x);
    u_xlat0.y = u_xlat0.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat20 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_2.xy = max(u_xlat0.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_2.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_31 = log2(abs(u_xlat16_0.z));
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_31 * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_31 = exp2(u_xlat16_31);
    u_xlat16_31 = min(u_xlat16_31, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_31) * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_31) * _GlossyEnvironmentColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_32 = u_xlat16_0.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_32 = max(u_xlat16_32, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_32 = min(u_xlat16_32, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_32 * u_xlat16_32;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat16_33 * u_xlat16_33 + 1.0;
    u_xlat10.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat10.x;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat10.xxx;
    u_xlat16_3.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_3.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_3.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat10.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat10.x = max(u_xlat10.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat10.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat10.x);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat10.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat10.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat16_3.x = abs(u_xlat16_3.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(u_xlat16_3.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat10.x = (-u_xlat16_3.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat10.x * u_xlat10.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_23 = u_xlat16_0.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_7 = u_xlat16_0.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_7 = u_xlat16_7 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-u_xlat16_23) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_23 = u_xlat16_23;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_23 = min(max(u_xlat16_23, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_23 = clamp(u_xlat16_23, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-u_xlat16_17.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-u_xlat16_32) + u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_17.x + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_17.x = min(max(u_xlat16_17.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_17.x = clamp(u_xlat16_17.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_23) * u_xlat5.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-u_xlat16_0.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_23) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat5.xyz) + u_xlat16_17.xxx;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xxx * u_xlat9.xyz + u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat34 = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat34 = inversesqrt(u_xlat34);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat34 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat34 = min(max(u_xlat34, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat34 = clamp(u_xlat34, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat35 = (-u_xlat34) * u_xlat34 + 1.0;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat16_33 * u_xlat34;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat34 * u_xlat34 + u_xlat35;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat16_33 / u_xlat34;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat34 * u_xlat34;
    u_xlat35 = u_xlat16_32 * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat16_32 + 1.0;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat6.x * u_xlat6.x;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat34 * u_xlat35;
    u_xlat34 = min(u_xlat34, 100.0);
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat34 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat34 = min(max(u_xlat34, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat34 = clamp(u_xlat34, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = min(u_xlat16_13.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_13.xyz + u_xlat16_17.xyz;
    u_xlat16_32 = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_32 = min(max(u_xlat16_32, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_32 = clamp(u_xlat16_32, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_32) + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_32 = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_32 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_32);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_32) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_32 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_13.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_32 = min(max(u_xlat16_32, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_32 = clamp(u_xlat16_32, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_32) * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = max(u_xlat16_13.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = min(u_xlat16_13.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_32 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_32 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_32);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_32) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = dot(u_xlat16_13.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_31 * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_11.x = (-u_xlat16_3.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat4.x = log2(u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat4.x = u_xlat4.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat4.x = exp2(u_xlat4.x);
    u_xlat4.x = (-u_xlat4.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat4.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat6.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_21 = (-u_xlat6.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_21 = u_xlat16_11.x * u_xlat16_21 + u_xlat34;
    u_xlat16_11.x = u_xlat16_11.x / u_xlat16_21;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_11.x * u_xlat16_1.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_11.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_11.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_11.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_11.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_11.x = u_xlat16_1.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_11.x;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = min(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_7) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat16_0.w;
    u_xlat0.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat0.x = min(u_xlat0.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat10.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat10.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat10.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat10.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat10.xy = u_xlat10.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat10.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat10.xy;
    u_xlat16_10 = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat10.xy).x;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat16_10 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat0.x = (-u_xlat0.x) + u_xlat10.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat0.x = min(max(u_xlat0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_31 = (-u_xlat0.x) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_31) + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}
SubProgram "gles " {
Keywords { "ENABLE_POST_TONE" "_DEBUG_OFF" "_ENVIRONMENTREFLECTIONS_OFF" "_IFFUR_OFF" "_IFRAMP_OFF" "_SHTYPE_LERP" }
"// hash: f432eaea81c06526
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
uniform 	mediump float _FurTilling;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT

#ifdef GL_FRAGMENT_PRECISION_HIGH

precision highp int;
uniform 	float _DigiChange;

#define SV_Target0 gl_FragData[0]
vec2 u_xlat0;
lowp vec4 u_xlat10_0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
mediump float u_xlat16_7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
vec2 u_xlat10;
lowp float u_xlat10_10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
vec3 u_xlat16;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_17;
float u_xlat20;
mediump float u_xlat16_21;
mediump float u_xlat16_23;
mediump float u_xlat16_31;
mediump float u_xlat16_32;
mediump float u_xlat16_33;
float u_xlat34;
float u_xlat35;
void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0.xyz = texture2D(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.xy = u_xlat16_1.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyw = u_xlat16_1.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyw;
    u_xlat16_31 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_31 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_31);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_31) * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_1.y * u_xlat16_1.y;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat16_1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat20 = u_xlat0.x * 0.125 + u_xlat10.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat10.x);
    u_xlat0.y = u_xlat0.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat20 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_2.xy = max(u_xlat0.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_2.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_31 = log2(abs(u_xlat10_0.z));
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_31 * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_31 = exp2(u_xlat16_31);
    u_xlat16_31 = min(u_xlat16_31, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_31) * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_31) * _GlossyEnvironmentColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_32 = u_xlat10_0.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_32 = max(u_xlat16_32, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_32 = min(u_xlat16_32, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_32 * u_xlat16_32;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat16_33 * u_xlat16_33 + 1.0;
    u_xlat10.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat10.x;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat10.xxx;
    u_xlat16_3.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_3.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_3.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat10.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat10.x = max(u_xlat10.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat10.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat10.x);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat10.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat10.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat16_3.x = abs(u_xlat16_3.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(u_xlat16_3.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat10.x = (-u_xlat16_3.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat10.x * u_xlat10.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_23 = u_xlat10_0.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_7 = u_xlat10_0.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_7 = u_xlat16_7 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-u_xlat16_23) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_23 = u_xlat16_23;
    u_xlat16_23 = clamp(u_xlat16_23, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-u_xlat16_17.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-u_xlat16_32) + u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_17.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17.x = clamp(u_xlat16_17.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_23) * u_xlat5.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-u_xlat10_0.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_23) + u_xlat10_0.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat5.xyz) + u_xlat16_17.xxx;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xxx * u_xlat9.xyz + u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat34 = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat34 = inversesqrt(u_xlat34);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat34 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat34 = clamp(u_xlat34, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat35 = (-u_xlat34) * u_xlat34 + 1.0;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat16_33 * u_xlat34;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat34 * u_xlat34 + u_xlat35;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat16_33 / u_xlat34;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat34 * u_xlat34;
    u_xlat35 = u_xlat16_32 * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat16_32 + 1.0;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat6.x * u_xlat6.x;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat34 * u_xlat35;
    u_xlat34 = min(u_xlat34, 100.0);
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat34 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat34 = clamp(u_xlat34, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = min(u_xlat16_13.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_13.xyz + u_xlat16_17.xyz;
    u_xlat16_32 = _SHshadow + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_32 = clamp(u_xlat16_32, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_32) + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_32 = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_32 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_32);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_32) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_32 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_13.xyz);
    u_xlat16_32 = clamp(u_xlat16_32, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_32) * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = max(u_xlat16_13.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = min(u_xlat16_13.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_32 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_32 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_32);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_32) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = dot(u_xlat16_13.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_31 * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_11.x = (-u_xlat16_3.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat4.x = log2(u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat4.x = u_xlat4.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat4.x = exp2(u_xlat4.x);
    u_xlat4.x = (-u_xlat4.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat4.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat6.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_21 = (-u_xlat6.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_21 = u_xlat16_11.x * u_xlat16_21 + u_xlat34;
    u_xlat16_11.x = u_xlat16_11.x / u_xlat16_21;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_11.x * u_xlat16_1.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_11.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_11.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_11.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_11.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_11.x = u_xlat16_1.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_11.x;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat10_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = min(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_7) * u_xlat10_0.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat10_0.w;
    u_xlat0.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat0.x = min(u_xlat0.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat10.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat10.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat10.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat10.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat10.xy = u_xlat10.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat10.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat10.xy;
    u_xlat10_10 = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat10.xy).x;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat10_10 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat0.x = (-u_xlat0.x) + u_xlat10.x;
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_31 = (-u_xlat0.x) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_31) + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    return;
}

	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _viweoffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHshadow;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _RimLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MatMapMul;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

#endif

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _RampTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
float u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
vec3 u_xlat11;
mediump float u_xlat16_11;
float u_xlat12;
mediump float u_xlat16_14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
mediump float u_xlat16_20;
mediump float u_xlat16_24;
mediump float u_xlat16_25;
mediump float u_xlat16_30;
float u_xlat32;
float u_xlat33;
mediump float u_xlat16_34;
float u_xlat36;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1 = max(u_xlat1, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1 = inversesqrt(u_xlat1);
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(u_xlat1);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(u_xlat1) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.xy = u_xlat16_0.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyw = u_xlat16_0.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyw;
    u_xlat16_30 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_30 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_30);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_30) * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_30 = dot((-u_xlat11.xyz), u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_30 + u_xlat16_30;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_30)) + (-u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_30 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_30 = abs(u_xlat16_30) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_30 = min(u_xlat16_30, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_34 = max(u_xlat16_34, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_34 = min(u_xlat16_34, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-u_xlat16_34) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_3 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_3.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = exp2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_5.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_1.z));
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_5.x = exp2(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_5.x = min(u_xlat16_5.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xxx;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_34;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_15.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat11.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat11.x;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat11.xxx;
    u_xlat11.x = (-u_xlat16_30) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat11.x * u_xlat11.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_24 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_25 = (-u_xlat16_14) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_14;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_14 = min(max(u_xlat16_14, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_14 = clamp(u_xlat16_14, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_25 = (-u_xlat16_25) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_25 = (-u_xlat16_34) + u_xlat16_25;
    u_xlat16_25 = u_xlat16_25 + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_25 = min(max(u_xlat16_25, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_25 = clamp(u_xlat16_25, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_14) * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-u_xlat16_1.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_14) + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_25) + (-u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat8.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat16_0.y * u_xlat16_0.y;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat16_0.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat32 * 0.125 + u_xlat33;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat32 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat33);
    u_xlat8.y = u_xlat32 + 0.125;
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat36 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat8.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat32 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat32 = inversesqrt(u_xlat32);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat32) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat2.x = min(max(u_xlat2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat2.x = clamp(u_xlat2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat12 = (-u_xlat2.x) * u_xlat2.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * u_xlat2.x + u_xlat12;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_15.x / u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat16_34 * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat2.z = u_xlat16_34 + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.xz = u_xlat2.xz * u_xlat2.xz;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * u_xlat12;
    u_xlat2.x = min(u_xlat2.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat33;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat6.x = min(max(u_xlat6.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat6.x = clamp(u_xlat6.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat33 * 0.5 + 0.5;
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xyw * u_xlat6.xxx;
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xyw * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xyw * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat6.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyw = u_xlat6.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_4.xyw = min(u_xlat16_4.xyw, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat2.xyw * u_xlat16_4.xyw;
    u_xlat8.y = 0.5;
    u_xlat16_2.xyw = texture(_RampTex, u_xlat8.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyw * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyw = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyw + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15.x = min(max(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.xyw = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat16_15.xxx + u_xlat16_4.xyw;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_15.x);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_15.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15.x = min(max(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyw * u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = max(u_xlat16_15.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = min(u_xlat16_15.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyw = u_xlat16_4.xyw + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_15.x);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.x = dot(u_xlat16_15.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_0.x = min(max(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_10.x = (-u_xlat16_30) + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = log2(u_xlat16_30);
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat2.x = exp2(u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat2.x = (-u_xlat2.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat2.z * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_20 = (-u_xlat2.z) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_20 = u_xlat16_10.x * u_xlat16_20 + u_xlat3.x;
    u_xlat16_10.x = u_xlat16_10.x / u_xlat16_20;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_10.x * u_xlat16_0.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_10.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_10.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_10.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_10.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_0.x = min(max(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_10.x = u_xlat16_0.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_10.x;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_0.xxx;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = max(u_xlat16_0.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = min(u_xlat16_0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyw;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat16_1.w;
    u_xlat1 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat1 = min(u_xlat1, 1.0);
    u_xlat11.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat11.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 * u_xlat11.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat11.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat11.xy = u_xlat11.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat11.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat11.xy;
    u_xlat16_11 = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat11.xy).x;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat16_11 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat1 = (-u_xlat1) + u_xlat11.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1 = min(max(u_xlat1, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1 = clamp(u_xlat1, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(u_xlat1);
    u_xlat16_30 = (-u_xlat1) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat2.xyw * vec3(u_xlat16_30) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    return;
}

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;

void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;

    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
