UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
vec3 u_xlat11;
float u_xlat12;
mediump float u_xlat16_14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
mediump float u_xlat16_20;
float u_xlat22;
mediump float u_xlat16_22;
mediump float u_xlat16_24;
mediump float u_xlat16_25;
mediump float u_xlat16_30;
float u_xlat31;
float u_xlat32;
float u_xlat33;
mediump float u_xlat16_34;
float u_xlat36;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.xy = u_xlat16_0.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyw = u_xlat16_0.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyw;
    u_xlat16_30 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_30 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_30);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_30) * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_30 = dot((-u_xlat11.xyz), u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_30 + u_xlat16_30;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_30)) + (-u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_30 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_30 = abs(u_xlat16_30) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_30 = min(u_xlat16_30, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_34 = max(u_xlat16_34, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_34 = min(u_xlat16_34, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-u_xlat16_34) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_3 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_3.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = exp2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_5.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_1.z));
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_5.x = exp2(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_5.x = min(u_xlat16_5.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xxx;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_34;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_15.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat11.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat11.x;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat11.xxx;
    u_xlat11.x = (-u_xlat16_30) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat11.x * u_xlat11.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_24 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_25 = (-u_xlat16_14) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_14;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_14 = min(max(u_xlat16_14, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_14 = clamp(u_xlat16_14, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_25 = (-u_xlat16_25) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_25 = (-u_xlat16_34) + u_xlat16_25;
    u_xlat16_25 = u_xlat16_25 + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_25 = min(max(u_xlat16_25, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_25 = clamp(u_xlat16_25, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_14) * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-u_xlat16_1.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_14) + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_25) + (-u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat8.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat16_0.y * u_xlat16_0.y;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat16_0.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat32 * 0.125 + u_xlat33;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat32 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat33);
    u_xlat8.y = u_xlat32 + 0.125;
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat36 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat8.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat32 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat32 = inversesqrt(u_xlat32);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat32) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat2.x = min(max(u_xlat2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat2.x = clamp(u_xlat2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat12 = (-u_xlat2.x) * u_xlat2.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * u_xlat2.x + u_xlat12;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_15.x / u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat16_34 * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat2.z = u_xlat16_34 + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.xz = u_xlat2.xz * u_xlat2.xz;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * u_xlat12;
    u_xlat2.x = min(u_xlat2.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat33 = min(max(u_xlat33, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat33 = clamp(u_xlat33, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xyw * vec3(u_xlat33);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xyw * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xyw * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat6.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = min(u_xlat16_7.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat2.xyw * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyw = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_15.x);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_15.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15.x = min(max(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyw * u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = max(u_xlat16_15.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = min(u_xlat16_15.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyw = u_xlat16_4.xyw + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_15.x);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.x = dot(u_xlat16_15.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_0.x = min(max(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_10.x = (-u_xlat16_30) + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = log2(u_xlat16_30);
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat2.x = exp2(u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat2.x = (-u_xlat2.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat2.z * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_20 = (-u_xlat2.z) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_20 = u_xlat16_10.x * u_xlat16_20 + u_xlat3.x;
    u_xlat16_10.x = u_xlat16_10.x / u_xlat16_20;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_10.x * u_xlat16_0.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_10.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_10.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_10.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_10.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_0.x = min(max(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_10.x = u_xlat16_0.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_10.x;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_0.xxx;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = max(u_xlat16_0.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = min(u_xlat16_0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyw;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat16_1.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat3.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz / u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat1 = min(u_xlat1, vec4(100.0, 100.0, 100.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat22 = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat22 = u_xlat22 + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat31 = u_xlat1.w * u_xlat22 + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat22 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat3.xy = vec2(u_xlat22) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat3.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat3.xy;
    u_xlat16_22 = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat3.xy).x;
    u_xlat22 = u_xlat16_22 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat31 = (-u_xlat31) + u_xlat22;

    u_xlat31 = min(max(u_xlat31, 0.0), 1.0);
#else

#endif
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat31) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_30 = (-u_xlat31) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat2.xyw * vec3(u_xlat16_30) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    return;
}

{

    u_xlat16_25 = (-u_xlat16_34) + u_xlat16_25;
    u_xlat16_25 = u_xlat16_25 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_25 = clamp(u_xlat16_25, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_14) * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-u_xlat10_1.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_14) + u_xlat10_1.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_25) + (-u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat8.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat16_0.y * u_xlat16_0.y;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat16_0.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat32 * 0.125 + u_xlat33;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat32 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat33);
    u_xlat8.y = u_xlat32 + 0.125;
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat36 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat8.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = _SHshadow + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat32 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat32 = inversesqrt(u_xlat32);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat32) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat2.x = clamp(u_xlat2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat12 = (-u_xlat2.x) * u_xlat2.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * u_xlat2.x + u_xlat12;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_15.x / u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat16_34 * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat2.z = u_xlat16_34 + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.xz = u_xlat2.xz * u_xlat2.xz;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * u_xlat12;
    u_xlat2.x = min(u_xlat2.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat33 = clamp(u_xlat33, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xyw * vec3(u_xlat33);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xyw * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xyw * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat6.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = min(u_xlat16_7.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat2.xyw * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyw = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_15.x);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_15.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyw * u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = max(u_xlat16_15.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = min(u_xlat16_15.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyw = u_xlat16_4.xyw + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_15.x);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.x = dot(u_xlat16_15.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_10.x = (-u_xlat16_30) + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = log2(u_xlat16_30);
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat2.x = exp2(u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat2.x = (-u_xlat2.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat2.z * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_20 = (-u_xlat2.z) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_20 = u_xlat16_10.x * u_xlat16_20 + u_xlat3.x;
    u_xlat16_10.x = u_xlat16_10.x / u_xlat16_20;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_10.x * u_xlat16_0.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_10.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_10.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_10.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_10.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_10.x = u_xlat16_0.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_10.x;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat10_1.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_0.xxx;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = max(u_xlat16_0.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = min(u_xlat16_0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyw;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat10_1.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat10_1.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat3.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz / u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat1 = min(u_xlat1, vec4(100.0, 100.0, 100.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat22 = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat22 = u_xlat22 + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat31 = u_xlat1.w * u_xlat22 + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat22 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat3.xy = vec2(u_xlat22) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat3.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat3.xy;
    u_xlat10_22 = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat3.xy).x;
    u_xlat22 = u_xlat10_22 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat31 = (-u_xlat31) + u_xlat22;
    u_xlat31 = clamp(u_xlat31, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat31) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_30 = (-u_xlat31) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat2.xyw * vec3(u_xlat16_30) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;

void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);

    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;

    u_xlat16_30 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_30 = abs(u_xlat16_30) + 0.00400000019;

    u_xlat16_5.x = exp2(u_xlat16_5.x);

    u_xlat11.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat11.x;

    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat11.x * u_xlat11.x;

    u_xlat16_14 = min(max(u_xlat16_14, 0.0), 1.0);

#endif
    u_xlat16_25 = (-u_xlat16_25) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_25 = (-u_xlat16_34) + u_xlat16_25;
    u_xlat16_25 = u_xlat16_25 + 1.0;

    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat16_0.y * u_xlat16_0.y;

    u_xlat36 = u_xlat32 * 0.125 + u_xlat33;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat32 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat33);

    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat36 + 0.125;

    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = _SHshadow + 1.0;

    u_xlat32 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat32 = inversesqrt(u_xlat32);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat32) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);

    u_xlat2.x = min(max(u_xlat2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat2.x = clamp(u_xlat2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat12 = (-u_xlat2.x) * u_xlat2.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * u_xlat2.x + u_xlat12;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_15.x / u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat16_34 * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat2.z = u_xlat16_34 + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.xz = u_xlat2.xz * u_xlat2.xz;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * u_xlat12;
    u_xlat2.x = min(u_xlat2.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);

    u_xlat33 = min(max(u_xlat33, 0.0), 1.0);

    u_xlat33 = clamp(u_xlat33, 0.0, 1.0);

    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xyw * vec3(u_xlat33);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xyw * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xyw * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat6.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = min(u_xlat16_7.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat2.xyw * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyw = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_15.x);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_15.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15.x = min(max(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyw * u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = max(u_xlat16_15.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = min(u_xlat16_15.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyw = u_xlat16_4.xyw + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_15.x);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.x = dot(u_xlat16_15.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_0.x = min(max(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_10.x = (-u_xlat16_30) + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = log2(u_xlat16_30);
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat2.x = exp2(u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat2.x = (-u_xlat2.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat2.z * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_20 = (-u_xlat2.z) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_20 = u_xlat16_10.x * u_xlat16_20 + u_xlat3.x;
    u_xlat16_10.x = u_xlat16_10.x / u_xlat16_20;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_10.x * u_xlat16_0.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_10.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_10.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_10.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_10.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_0.x = min(max(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_10.x = u_xlat16_0.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_10.x;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_0.xxx;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = max(u_xlat16_0.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = min(u_xlat16_0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyw;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat16_1.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);

    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz / u_xlat3.xyz;

    u_xlat1 = min(u_xlat1, vec4(100.0, 100.0, 100.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat22 = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat22 = u_xlat22 + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat31 = u_xlat1.w * u_xlat22 + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat22 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat3.xy = vec2(u_xlat22) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat3.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat3.xy;
    u_xlat16_22 = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat3.xy).x;
    u_xlat22 = u_xlat16_22 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat31 = (-u_xlat31) + u_xlat22;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat31 = min(max(u_xlat31, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat31 = clamp(u_xlat31, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat31) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_30 = (-u_xlat31) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat2.xyw * vec3(u_xlat16_30) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;

SubProgram "gles " {
Keywords { "_DEBUG_OFF" "_IFFUR_OFF" "_IFRAMP_OFF" "_SHTYPE_LERP" }
"// hash: 888eaf9dfa5fc2
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];

attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;

vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT
#version 100

#ifdef GL_FRAGMENT_PRECISION_HIGH
    precision highp float;
#else
    precision mediump float;
#endif
precision highp int;
uniform 	float _DigiChange;
uniform 	vec4 _DigiBaseColor0;
uniform 	vec4 _DigiBaseColor1;
uniform 	vec4 _DigiST1;
uniform 	float _DigiPow;
uniform 	vec4 _MainLightPosition;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightColor;
uniform 	vec4 _Time;
uniform 	mediump vec4 unity_SpecCube0_HDR;
uniform 	mediump float _Emissive;
uniform 	mediump float _RoughNessOffset;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _SpecularColor;
uniform 	mediump float _MetallicOffset;
uniform 	mediump float _NormalScale;
uniform 	mediump float _EmisssionScale;
uniform 	mediump float _SHScale;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _SHTopColor;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _SHBotColor;
uniform 	mediump vec3 _AddLightDir;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _AddlightColor;
uniform 	mediump float _RimlightScale;
uniform 	mediump float _RimlightScale2;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _RimlightColor;
uniform 	mediump float _AOScale;
uniform 	mediump float _SHshadow;
uniform 	vec4 _RimLightDir;
uniform lowp sampler2D _MainTex;
uniform lowp sampler2D _MixMap;
uniform lowp sampler2D _BumpMap;
uniform lowp samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
uniform lowp sampler2D _ClothTex;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
#define SV_Target0 gl_FragData[0]
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
lowp vec4 u_xlat10_1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
lowp vec4 u_xlat10_3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
vec3 u_xlat11;
float u_xlat12;
mediump float u_xlat16_14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
mediump float u_xlat16_20;
float u_xlat22;
lowp float u_xlat10_22;
mediump float u_xlat16_24;
mediump float u_xlat16_25;
mediump float u_xlat16_30;
float u_xlat31;
float u_xlat32;
float u_xlat33;
mediump float u_xlat16_34;
float u_xlat36;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat10_3.xyz = texture2D(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat10_3.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.xy = u_xlat16_0.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyw = u_xlat16_0.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyw;
    u_xlat16_30 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_30 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_30);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_30) * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_30 = dot((-u_xlat11.xyz), u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_30 + u_xlat16_30;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_30)) + (-u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_30 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_30 = abs(u_xlat16_30) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_30 = min(u_xlat16_30, 1.0);
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat10_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_34 = max(u_xlat16_34, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_34 = min(u_xlat16_34, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_5.x = (-u_xlat16_34) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * 6.0;
    u_xlat10_3 = textureCube(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat10_3.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = exp2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat10_3.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_5.x = log2(abs(u_xlat10_1.z));
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_5.x = exp2(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat16_5.x = min(u_xlat16_5.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xxx;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_34;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_15.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat11.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat11.x;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat11.xxx;
    u_xlat11.x = (-u_xlat16_30) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat11.x * u_xlat11.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat10_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat10_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_24 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_25 = (-u_xlat16_14) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_14;
    u_xlat16_14 = clamp(u_xlat16_14, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_25 = (-u_xlat16_25) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_25 = (-u_xlat16_34) + u_xlat16_25;
    u_xlat16_25 = u_xlat16_25 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_25 = clamp(u_xlat16_25, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_14) * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-u_xlat10_1.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_14) + u_xlat10_1.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_25) + (-u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat8.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat16_0.y * u_xlat16_0.y;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat16_0.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat32 * 0.125 + u_xlat33;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat32 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat33);
    u_xlat8.y = u_xlat32 + 0.125;
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat36 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat8.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = _SHshadow + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat32 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat32 = inversesqrt(u_xlat32);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat32) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat2.x = clamp(u_xlat2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat12 = (-u_xlat2.x) * u_xlat2.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * u_xlat2.x + u_xlat12;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_15.x / u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat16_34 * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat2.z = u_xlat16_34 + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.xz = u_xlat2.xz * u_xlat2.xz;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * u_xlat12;
    u_xlat2.x = min(u_xlat2.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat33 = clamp(u_xlat33, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xyw * vec3(u_xlat33);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xyw * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xyw * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat6.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = min(u_xlat16_7.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat2.xyw * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyw = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_15.x);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_15.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyw * u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = max(u_xlat16_15.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = min(u_xlat16_15.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyw = u_xlat16_4.xyw + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_15.x);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.x = dot(u_xlat16_15.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_10.x = (-u_xlat16_30) + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = log2(u_xlat16_30);
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat2.x = exp2(u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat2.x = (-u_xlat2.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat2.z * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_20 = (-u_xlat2.z) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_20 = u_xlat16_10.x * u_xlat16_20 + u_xlat3.x;
    u_xlat16_10.x = u_xlat16_10.x / u_xlat16_20;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_10.x * u_xlat16_0.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_10.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_10.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_10.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_10.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_10.x = u_xlat16_0.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_10.x;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat10_1.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_0.xxx;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = max(u_xlat16_0.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = min(u_xlat16_0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyw;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat10_1.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat10_1.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat3.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz / u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat1 = min(u_xlat1, vec4(100.0, 100.0, 100.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat22 = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat22 = u_xlat22 + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat31 = u_xlat1.w * u_xlat22 + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat22 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat3.xy = vec2(u_xlat22) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat3.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat3.xy;
    u_xlat10_22 = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat3.xy).x;
    u_xlat22 = u_xlat10_22 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat31 = (-u_xlat31) + u_xlat22;
    u_xlat31 = clamp(u_xlat31, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat31) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_30 = (-u_xlat31) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat2.xyw * vec3(u_xlat16_30) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    return;
}

}

}
 Pass {
  Name "OUTLINE"
  LOD 300
  Tags { "IGNOREPROJECTOR" = "true" "LIGHTMODE" = "AdvancedOutline" "QUEUE" = "Geometry" "RenderPipeline" = "LightweightPipeline" "RenderType" = "[_RenderType]" }
  Cull Front
  GpuProgramID 110026
Program "vp" {
SubProgram "gles " {
Keywords { "_VCOLOR2N_OFF" "_VTEX_OFF" }
"// hash: 7372a2dfa20d9f7c
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec4 _ScreenParams;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 _OutlineColor;
uniform 	mediump float _Offset;
uniform 	vec4 _lightDir;
uniform 	vec4 _ScreenResolution;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_COLOR0;
varying mediump float vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat6;
float u_xlat9;
float u_xlat10;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = 0.0;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = max(u_xlat9, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(_lightDir.xyz, _lightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * _lightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-_OutlineColor.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat3.xyz + _OutlineColor.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * in_COLOR0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_NORMAL0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_NORMAL0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_NORMAL0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xz = u_xlat0.yy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].xy * u_xlat0.xx + u_xlat3.xz;
    u_xlat0.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].xy * u_xlat0.zz + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat6 = dot(u_xlat0.xy, u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlat6 = inversesqrt(u_xlat6);
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(u_xlat6) * u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy / _ScreenParams.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy * _ScreenResolution.yy;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat1.y * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].w;
    u_xlat6 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].w * u_xlat1.x + u_xlat6;
    u_xlat6 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].w * u_xlat1.z + u_xlat6;
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat6 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].w;
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(u_xlat6) * u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy * vec2(0.00462962966, 0.00462962966);
    u_xlat2.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[0].x;
    u_xlat2.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[1].y;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy / u_xlat2.xy;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat1.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[0].xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[2].xyz * u_xlat1.zzz + u_xlat1.xyw;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat0.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat0.xy, u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlat0.x = sqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 0.00100000005);
    u_xlat3.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat3.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat3.x);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xxx * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz / abs(u_xlat3.zzz);
    u_xlat10 = abs(_Offset) * 0.150000006;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat10;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 100.0;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[0].z;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[1].z;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].z;
    u_xlat1.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].z;
    u_xlat0.w = 1.0;
    gl_Position.z = dot(u_xlat1, u_xlat0);
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[0].x;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].x;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].x;
    gl_Position.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[1].y;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].y;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].y;
    gl_Position.y = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat0.yzw);
    u_xlat0.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].w;
    u_xlat0.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].w;
    gl_Position.w = dot(u_xlat0.xy, u_xlat0.zw);
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT
#version 100

#ifdef GL_FRAGMENT_PRECISION_HIGH
    precision highp float;
#else
    precision mediump float;
#endif
precision highp int;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
#define SV_Target0 gl_FragData[0]
void main()
{
    SV_Target0.xyz = max(vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _OutlineWidth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Offset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _lightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _FarWidth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _NearWidth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _color1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _ScreenResolution;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _OutlineMap;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec4 in_COLOR0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump float vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat6;
float u_xlat9;
float u_xlat10;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = 0.0;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = max(u_xlat9, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(_lightDir.xyz, _lightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * _lightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat0.x = min(max(u_xlat0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-_OutlineColor.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat3.xyz + _OutlineColor.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * in_COLOR0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_NORMAL0.zxy * in_TANGENT0.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_NORMAL0.yzx * in_TANGENT0.zxy + (-u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * in_TANGENT0.www;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * unity_WorldTransformParams.www;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_COLOR0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat1.yyy;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_TANGENT0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * u_xlat1.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat3.xz = u_xlat0.yy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].xy * u_xlat0.xx + u_xlat3.xz;
    u_xlat0.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].xy * u_xlat0.zz + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat6 = dot(u_xlat0.xy, u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlat6 = inversesqrt(u_xlat6);
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(u_xlat6) * u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy / _ScreenParams.xy;
    u_xlat6 = textureLod(_OutlineMap, in_TEXCOORD0.xy, 0.0).w;
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(u_xlat6) * u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy * _ScreenResolution.yy;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat1.y * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].w;
    u_xlat6 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].w * u_xlat1.x + u_xlat6;
    u_xlat6 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].w * u_xlat1.z + u_xlat6;
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat6 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].w;
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(u_xlat6) * u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy * vec2(0.00462962966, 0.00462962966);
    u_xlat2.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[0].x;
    u_xlat2.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[1].y;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy / u_xlat2.xy;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat1.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[0].xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[2].xyz * u_xlat1.zzz + u_xlat1.xyw;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat0.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat0.xy, u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlat0.x = sqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 0.00100000005);
    u_xlat3.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat3.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat3.x);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xxx * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz / abs(u_xlat3.zzz);
    u_xlat10 = abs(_Offset) * 0.150000006;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat10;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 100.0;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[0].z;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[1].z;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].z;
    u_xlat1.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].z;
    u_xlat0.w = 1.0;
    gl_Position.z = dot(u_xlat1, u_xlat0);
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[0].x;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].x;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].x;
    gl_Position.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[1].y;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].y;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].y;
    gl_Position.y = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat0.yzw);
    u_xlat0.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].w;
    u_xlat0.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].w;
    gl_Position.w = dot(u_xlat0.xy, u_xlat0.zw);
    return;
}

in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;

out mediump float vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;

void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = 0.0;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = max(u_xlat9, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat0.xyz;

#version 300 es

#define HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS 1
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
#define UNITY_UNIFORM
#else
#define UNITY_UNIFORM uniform
#endif
#define UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION 1
#if UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x) layout(location = x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(binding = x, std140)
#else
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(std140)
#endif
uniform 	vec4 _ScreenParams;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerDraw {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LODFade;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightData;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightIndices[2];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_ProbesOcclusion;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SpecCube0_HDR;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_DynamicLightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHC;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(1) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _OutlineColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _OutlineWidth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Offset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _lightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _FarWidth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _NearWidth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _color1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _ScreenResolution;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _OutlineMap;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec4 in_COLOR0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump float vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat6;
float u_xlat9;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = 0.0;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = max(u_xlat9, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(_lightDir.xyz, _lightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * _lightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat0.x = min(max(u_xlat0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-_OutlineColor.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat3.xyz + _OutlineColor.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = textureLod(_OutlineMap, in_TEXCOORD0.xy, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_NORMAL0.zxy * in_TANGENT0.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_NORMAL0.yzx * in_TANGENT0.zxy + (-u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * in_TANGENT0.www;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * unity_WorldTransformParams.www;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_COLOR0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat1.yyy;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_TANGENT0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * u_xlat1.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat3.xz = u_xlat0.yy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].xy * u_xlat0.xx + u_xlat3.xz;
    u_xlat0.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].xy * u_xlat0.zz + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat6 = dot(u_xlat0.xy, u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlat6 = inversesqrt(u_xlat6);
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(u_xlat6) * u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy / _ScreenParams.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat1.ww * u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.z = u_xlat1.w * abs(_Offset);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy * _ScreenResolution.yy;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat1.y * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].w;
    u_xlat9 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].w * u_xlat1.x + u_xlat9;
    u_xlat9 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].w * u_xlat1.z + u_xlat9;
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat9 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].w;
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(u_xlat9) * u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.00462962966, 0.00462962966, 0.150000006);
    u_xlat2.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[0].x;
    u_xlat2.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[1].y;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy / u_xlat2.xy;
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat0.xy, u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlat9 = sqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat9 = max(u_xlat9, 0.00100000005);
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat9 * u_xlat0.z;
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat6 * 100.0;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat1.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[0].xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[2].xyz * u_xlat1.zzz + u_xlat1.xyw;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat0.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.xyw = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = u_xlat0.xyw / abs(u_xlat0.www);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyw * vec3(u_xlat6) + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[0].z;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[1].z;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].z;
    u_xlat1.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].z;
    u_xlat0.w = 1.0;
    gl_Position.z = dot(u_xlat1, u_xlat0);
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[0].x;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].x;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].x;
    gl_Position.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[1].y;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].y;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].y;
    gl_Position.y = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat0.yzw);
    u_xlat0.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].w;
    u_xlat0.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].w;
    gl_Position.w = dot(u_xlat0.xy, u_xlat0.zw);
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT
#version 300 es

precision highp float;
precision highp int;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
void main()
{
    SV_Target0.xyz = max(vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec4 _Time;
uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	vec4 _DigiST1;
uniform 	mediump float _DigiChange;
uniform 	float _DigiScale;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_COLOR0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD2;
vec4 u_xlat0;
mediump float u_xlat16_1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat12;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = vec2(0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat12 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat12 = max(u_xlat12, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat12 = inversesqrt(u_xlat12);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat12) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_1 = min(u_xlat16_1, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1 = (-u_xlat16_1) + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(0.0500000007, 0.0500000007, 0.0500000007);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_1) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * vec3(_DigiScale) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat2.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat2.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat2.zzz + u_xlat2.xyw;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-u_xlat2.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat0.w = clamp(u_xlat0.w, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_COLOR0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0.x = in_TEXCOORD0.y * 2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat0.z = (-_DigiChange) * 2.0 + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.z = clamp(u_xlat0.z, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyw = in_TEXCOORD0.xyy;
    vs_TEXCOORD2 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat2.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat2.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat2.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

#ifdef FRAGMENT
#version 100

#ifdef GL_FRAGMENT_PRECISION_HIGH
    precision highp float;
#else
    precision mediump float;
#endif
precision highp int;
uniform 	mediump float _DigiChange;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _DigiBaseColor0;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _DigiBaseColor1;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _DigiHighColor;
uniform lowp sampler2D _ClothTex;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD2;
#define SV_Target0 gl_FragData[0]
float u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
lowp vec2 u_xlat10_3;
bool u_xlatb9;
mediump float u_xlat16_10;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0 = vs_TEXCOORD1.w * vs_TEXCOORD2.w;
    u_xlat16_1.x = _DigiChange;
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2 = (-_DigiBaseColor0) + _DigiBaseColor1;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1.xxxx * u_xlat16_2 + _DigiBaseColor0;
    u_xlat10_3.xy = texture2D(_ClothTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xy;
    u_xlatb9 = u_xlat16_1.w>=u_xlat10_3.x;
    u_xlat16_10 = (u_xlatb9) ? u_xlat0 : 0.0;
    u_xlat16_10 = u_xlat10_3.x * u_xlat16_10;
    u_xlat16_2.x = _DigiChange + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat16_2.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat10_3.y * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * vs_TEXCOORD2.z;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _DigiHighColor.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_10) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#ifdef VERTEX

#define HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS 1
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
#define UNITY_UNIFORM
#else
#define UNITY_UNIFORM uniform
#endif
#define UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION 1
#if UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x) layout(location = x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(binding = x, std140)
#else
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(std140)
#endif
uniform 	vec4 _Time;
uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(1) uniform UnityPerDraw {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LODFade;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightData;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightIndices[2];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_ProbesOcclusion;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SpecCube0_HDR;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_DynamicLightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHC;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _OutlineColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _OutlineWidth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Offset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _lightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _ScreenResolution;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _DigiST1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DigiChange;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DigiBaseColor0;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DigiBaseColor1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DigiHighColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _DigiScale;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_COLOR0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD2;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat4;
bool u_xlatb4;
float u_xlat8;
float u_xlat12;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).y;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.z = 0.0;
    u_xlat4 = u_xlat0.x * in_TEXCOORD0.y + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.xy = min(u_xlat16_1.xx, vec2(1.0, 0.0));
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb4 = !!(u_xlat4>=u_xlat16_1.y);
#else
    u_xlatb4 = u_xlat4>=u_xlat16_1.y;
#endif
    u_xlat4 = u_xlatb4 ? 1.0 : float(0.0);
    u_xlat8 = (-u_xlat4) * u_xlat0.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat4;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_1.y * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (-u_xlat16_1.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.xyw = u_xlat0.xxx * in_NORMAL0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.w = u_xlat8;
    u_xlat2.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(0.0500000007, 0.0500000007, 0.0500000007);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * vec3(_DigiScale) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyw * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat12 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat12 = max(u_xlat12, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat12 = inversesqrt(u_xlat12);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat12) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.w = min(max(u_xlat1.w, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.w = clamp(u_xlat1.w, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_COLOR0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat12 = in_TEXCOORD0.y * 2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat1.z = (-_DigiChange) * 2.0 + u_xlat12;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.z = min(max(u_xlat1.z, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.z = clamp(u_xlat1.z, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.xyw = in_TEXCOORD0.xyy;
    vs_TEXCOORD2 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT
#version 300 es

precision highp float;
precision highp int;
#define HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS 1
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
#define UNITY_UNIFORM
#else
#define UNITY_UNIFORM uniform
#endif
#define UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION 1
#if UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x) layout(location = x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(binding = x, std140)
#else
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(std140)
#endif
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _OutlineColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _OutlineWidth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Offset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _lightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _ScreenResolution;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _DigiST1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DigiChange;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DigiBaseColor0;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DigiBaseColor1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DigiHighColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _DigiScale;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD2;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
float u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_3;
bool u_xlatb9;
mediump float u_xlat16_10;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0 = vs_TEXCOORD1.w * vs_TEXCOORD2.w;
    u_xlat16_1.x = _DigiChange;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2 = (-_DigiBaseColor0) + _DigiBaseColor1;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1.xxxx * u_xlat16_2 + _DigiBaseColor0;
    u_xlat16_3.xy = texture(_ClothTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xy;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb9 = !!(u_xlat16_1.w>=u_xlat16_3.x);
#else
    u_xlatb9 = u_xlat16_1.w>=u_xlat16_3.x;
#endif
    u_xlat16_10 = (u_xlatb9) ? u_xlat0 : 0.0;
    u_xlat16_10 = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_10;
    u_xlat16_2.x = _DigiChange + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat16_2.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_3.y * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * vs_TEXCOORD2.z;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _DigiHighColor.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_10) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"

    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).y;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.z = 0.0;
    u_xlat4 = u_xlat0.x * in_TEXCOORD0.y + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.xy = min(u_xlat16_1.xx, vec2(1.0, 0.0));
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb4 = !!(u_xlat4>=u_xlat16_1.y);
#else
    u_xlatb4 = u_xlat4>=u_xlat16_1.y;
#endif
    u_xlat4 = u_xlatb4 ? 1.0 : float(0.0);
    u_xlat8 = (-u_xlat4) * u_xlat0.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat4;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_1.y * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (-u_xlat16_1.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.xyw = u_xlat0.xxx * in_NORMAL0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.w = u_xlat8;
    u_xlat2.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(0.0500000007, 0.0500000007, 0.0500000007);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * vec3(_DigiScale) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyw * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat12 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat12 = max(u_xlat12, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat12 = inversesqrt(u_xlat12);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat12) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.w = min(max(u_xlat1.w, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.w = clamp(u_xlat1.w, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_COLOR0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat12 = in_TEXCOORD0.y * 2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat1.z = (-_DigiChange) * 2.0 + u_xlat12;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.z = min(max(u_xlat1.z, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.z = clamp(u_xlat1.z, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.xyw = in_TEXCOORD0.xyy;
    vs_TEXCOORD2 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

#endif

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DigiBaseColor1;

	UNITY_UNIFORM float _DigiScale;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD2;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
float u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_3;
bool u_xlatb9;
mediump float u_xlat16_10;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0 = vs_TEXCOORD1.w * vs_TEXCOORD2.w;
    u_xlat16_1.x = _DigiChange;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2 = (-_DigiBaseColor0) + _DigiBaseColor1;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1.xxxx * u_xlat16_2 + _DigiBaseColor0;
    u_xlat16_3.xy = texture(_ClothTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xy;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb9 = !!(u_xlat16_1.w>=u_xlat16_3.x);
#else
    u_xlatb9 = u_xlat16_1.w>=u_xlat16_3.x;
#endif
    u_xlat16_10 = (u_xlatb9) ? u_xlat0 : 0.0;
    u_xlat16_10 = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_10;
    u_xlat16_2.x = _DigiChange + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat16_2.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_3.y * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * vs_TEXCOORD2.z;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _DigiHighColor.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_10) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}
